label lb_day3_mc_wakesup:
    scene sc day3hotelmorning m08
    with flash
    mc"NICKY!!!"
    show sc day3hotelmorning m10
    mc"(Oh shit! It was only a nightmare‚Ä¶ Man, that was one shitty sleep.)"
    mc"(Why the hell did I have that kind of dream about [s_name] for??)"
    show sc day3hotelmorning m11
    mc"(I can‚Äôt quite remember everything that happened or whatever was said, but the pain in my stomach tells me it was definitely wrong.)"
    show sc day3hotelmorning m09
    mc"(And Nicole let me know what she really thought of me for having those kind of thoughts and feelings.)"
    show sc day3hotelmorning m10
    mc"(Why would I even think of [s_name] in that kind of way? What the hell is wrong with me?)"
    show sc day1hotelintro i03
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ I don‚Äôt think I heard [s_name] come home last night either. Perhaps she snuck in and I didn‚Äôt manage to hear her.)"
    mc"(I‚Äôm really not looking forward to talking to [s_name] about her time with Brodie last night.)"
    if v_day2_nicole_lie == False:
        # ‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player told Nicole the truth‚Äù"
        mc"(But I know at some point I‚Äôll have to.)"
        mc"(And I promised Nicole that I would at least try to be supportive of whatever decision [s_name] has made.)"
    else:
        # ‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player lied to Nicole‚Äù"
        mc"(But I know at some point I‚Äôll have to.)"
        mc"(I should at least try to be supportive of whatever decision [s_name] has made. It‚Äôs what Nicole would probably tell me to do.)"
        mc"(Damnit‚Ä¶ I better go and see if [s_name] is in her room, just to make sure she returned home safely‚Ä¶)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    # (MC stands outside F‚Äôs door)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3hotelmorning m01
    with dissolve
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Door_Knock_Sound_Effect_Free.mp3" fadein 1.0
    "(Knock, knock, knock)"
    stop sound fadeout 1.0
    show sc day3hotelmorning m02
    mc"[s_name], are you there?"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ No answer.)" 
    mc"(What if she‚Äôs sleeping and just didn‚Äôt hear me?)"
    mc"(Maybe I could sneak a peek in there real quick before she notices I‚Äôm in her room.)"
    # [Open the door]"
    # (MC opens the door to F‚Äôs room)"
    # (MC notices that F‚Äôs is not in her bed, and it is still made)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3hotelmorning m03
    with dissolve
    mc"(She‚Äôs not here, and her bed looks untouched.)"
    mc"(Which means she didn‚Äôt come home last night, and she more than likely stayed at her boyfriend‚Äôs place.)"
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # END SCENE"
    # NEXT SCENE: DAY 3 SOW 02 - MC at the lighthouse alone. Friend didn't return that morning."
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (MC sits in the kitchen, having some breakfast alone. He‚Äôs changed into casual clothing)"
    scene sc day3hotelmorning m04
    with dissolve
    mc"(Where the hell is she??)"
    mc"(It‚Äôs almost nine, and we should have already started work for the day.)"
    show sc day3hotelmorning m06
    mc"(I should probably try ringing her cell, just to see if she‚Äôs all right, and to find out if she‚Äôs coming back any time soon.)"
    # [Try to call her]"
    # (MC rings F‚Äôs number)"
    # (shows on the screen ‚ÄúNumber not available‚Äù)"
    show sc day3hotelmorning m07
    mc"(Damn‚Ä¶ Either [s_name]‚Äôs phone is switched off, or she‚Äôs run out of battery.)"
    mc"(How am I going to get in contact with her now?)"
    show sc day3hotelmorning m05
    mc"(Now I‚Äôm really concerned‚Ä¶)"
    show sc day3hotelmorning m06
    mc"(I wonder if I should call her mother, Ashley. Perhaps her cousin [c_name] knows how to get in touch with this guy Brodie.)"
    mc"(Maybe she knows where he lives in Sunshine Bay, or where he would‚Äôve taken [s_name] to dinner last night.)"
    mc"(Dammit‚Ä¶ I knew that this whole thing with this guy she‚Äôs been seeing felt a bit off‚Ä¶)"
    mc"(I have to try and remain positive, even though that small, pessimistic side of my head is fearing the worst, and something bad has happened to her‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)





label lb_day3_lucas_intro:
    #(These words come up on the screen, with a black background)"
    #"Meanwhile, across town‚Ä¶"
    scene bg acrosstown
    with dissolve
    scene bg acrosstown
    with Pause (4)
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3lucasintro l01
    with dissolve
    s"(Ohh.. My head...)"
    show sc day3lucasintro l03
    s"(Why does it have to be so damn hot out today?)"
    show sc day3lucasintro l04
    s"(Where the hell am I?)"
    s"(How could I manage to get myself lost in my own town??)"
    show sc day3lucasintro l05
    s"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    s"(I really regret taking that phone call from Brodie last night, and then going to dinner with him.)"
    show sc day3lucasintro l04
    s"(Not to mention what happened afterward.)"
    s"(How could I be so blind?)"
    s"(I should have known it was too good to be true, and that I should have listened to [y_name].)"
    s"(He may never forgive me for this.)"
    s"(Things were going so well between us, and with one bad decision on my behalf, it may have changed everything, changed our relationship.)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3lucasintro l06
    with dissolve
    s"(Hmm‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs kind of ironic that I should be walking past our old house at this very moment.)"
    show sc day3lucasintro l07
    jump lb_day3_lucas_intro_1

label lb_day3_lucas_intro_1:
    s"(Gerald saved me and Mom from having to live any longer in this rough neighbourhood...)"

label lb_day3_lucas_intro_2:
    s"(And then five years later Mom abandons him and [y_name].)"
    show sc day3lucasintro l08
    s"(I‚Äôm still angry at her for that, but right now I feel like I‚Äôm no better than her after abandoning [y_name] last night.) "
    show sc day3lucasintro l07
    s"(I really have to make it up to him, if he‚Äôll let me. [y_name] certainly deserves that after everything he‚Äôs gone through just to be here with me.)"
    s"(I just pray that he‚Äôll forgive me‚Ä¶ Again.)"
    show sc day3lucasintro l06
    s"(Okay, I think I know where I am now. I know my way home from here.)"
    show sc day3lucasintro l10
    s"(At least I haven‚Äôt passed any weirdos so far.) "
