    show sc day3lucasintro l09
    s"Go screw yourself, asshole!"
    show sc day3lucasintro l12
    lu"Hehe, I bet you could do all kinds of screwing baby."
    show sc day3lucasintro l11
    lu"What‚Äôs the matter sweet cheeks? Did Brodie leave you a little frustrated after last night?"
    lu"I can help you out with that you know."
    show sc day3lucasintro l09
    s"How on earth do you know Brodie?"
    show sc day3lucasintro l12
    lu"Oh I know all about Brodie. And all about you too‚Ä¶ [s_name]."
    show sc day3lucasintro l10
    s"(Oh shit! This guy knows my name.)"
    s"(Has he been following me ever since I left Brodie's place? Or even before then?)"
    s"(This is a really worrying situation.)"
    show sc day3lucasintro l09
    s"I‚Äôm warning you mister, I‚Äôm not in the mood for this right now."
    show sc day3lucasintro l13
    with vpunch
    s"Ohh!"
    show sc day3lucasintro l14
    lu"Hehehe!"
    show sc day3lucasintro l15
    lu"I have a feeling that you‚Äôre in the mood for all kinds of stuff gorgeous."
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)



















label lb_day3_jazmin_intro:
