    show sc day3jazzintro j23
    s"But I‚Äôm okay, thanks to you."
    show sc day3jazzintro j14
    jaz"Good to hear. I‚Äôm Jazmin by the way, but my friends call me Jazzy."
    show sc day3jazzintro j23
    s"Oh! I‚Äôm so sorry for not introducing myself. I‚Äôm [s_name]."
    # (the shakes hands)"
