label lb_day3_s_returns_home:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 05 - Friend returns home, gets upset when she sees the MC"
    # (Jazzy and Friend still walking and talking, mention the fight with Brodie)"
    scene sc day3jazzintro j29
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/03/01/Birds_in_trees_sounds_effects1.mp3" loop fadein 1.0
    s"So then we got in a fight, and I told him I was leaving."
    jaz"It sounds like you did the right thing. Boy, what a jerk!"
    show sc day3jazzintro j29
    jaz"How long did you say you‚Äôve been with this Brodie guy for?"
    s"A little over three years now."
    s"I thought he knew how I felt, but he couldn‚Äôt help but bring it up again, even though I asked him not to."
    s"He must‚Äôve thought that by buttering me up with a fancy restaurant for dinner and then having a couple of bottles of champagne, that I‚Äôd agree to anything he asked of me."
    show sc day3jazzintro j28
    jaz"Well good for you for standing your ground and telling him off."
    s"Thanks‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3jazzintro j59
    s"So, is this your first time to Sunshine Bay?"
    jaz"No, I actually went to one of the colleges here a few years ago."
    show sc day3jazzintro j27
    s"Oh really? I'm surprised that we've never crossed paths before as I went to the local college too."
    s"However, I never attained my degree. Did you?"
    jaz"Yes, I did, but not here in Sunshine Bay. I lived with my father for a couple of years and obtained my degree earlier this year."
    show sc day3jazzintro j28
    s"That's awesome!"
    jaz"I decided to come back to Sunshine Bay for work and because I enjoyed it so much the last time I was here."
    show sc day3jazzintro j29
    s"Well, hopefully you manage to do that."
    show sc day3jazzintro j28
    s"Oh, before I forget, there‚Äôs someone I‚Äôd like to introduce you to when we get to the hotel."
    jaz"Oh, who is it?"
    jump lb_day3_s_returns_home_1

label lb_day3_s_returns_home_1:
    s"A good friend of mine, [y_name]. We‚Äôve known each other since we were kids. "

label lb_day3_s_returns_home_2:
    s"He‚Äôs here from Darkham City and he‚Äôs staying at the hotel with me over the summer to help out."
    s"The hotel needs a lot of work, but [y_name] and I have put some plans in place to fix a lot of things up."
    show sc day3jazzintro j27
    jaz"He sounds like a really nice guy by the sound of things, given he‚Äôs travelled a long way to be here for the summer and to help you."
    show sc day3jazzintro j28
    s"Yeah, he sure is. And I‚Äôm also certain that he‚Äôs very worried about me."
    show sc day3jazzintro j29
    s"We kind of got into a fight just before I left for my date last night you see."
    s"He told me it wasn‚Äôt a good idea for me to go, and it turns out he was right."
