label lb_day3_brodie_meeting:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 06 - Business meeting hosted by Brodie's Dad, Gascoigne is there."
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (Gascoigne and the Boss arrive early at the meeting)"
    # (There‚Äôs a map of the lighthouse on the table - the boss is looking over it and planning what to do once they demolish the hotel)"
    scene sc day3bossmeeting b01
    with dissolve
    mg"So uh, should we get the meeting started boss?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b06
    tb"Not just yet, we still have a couple more to arrive."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b05
    tb"I have to say Mister Gascoigne, it‚Äôs a surprise not to see your face buried in your phone for a change!"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b02
    mg"Not really much point at the moment Boss, especially with the season suspended now for the foreseeable future."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b05
    tb"Ah yes, I did read about that."
    tb"Well look on the bright side, at least your team won‚Äôt be beaten over the next few months!"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b03
    mg"Haha, well that‚Äôs true!"
    # (Lucas walks in. Don‚Äôt show Lucas until this next line below)"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b09
    tb"Oh there you are, finally."
    tb"So how did it go this morning Lucas?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b12
    lu"Good boss, I followed her as you asked."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b09
    tb"And you didn‚Äôt attack her?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b11
    lu"No sir. But [s_name] knows I‚Äôm watching her now, so she may figure out that you‚Äôre onto her."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b07
    tb"That‚Äôs fine."
    tb"After Brodie had dinner with her last night, we just have to make sure that she has no plans to back out of selling her hotel."
    tb"I haven‚Äôt heard from Brodie yet, but I‚Äôm sure my son sealed the deal last night."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b13
    lu"Uh, boss‚Ä¶?"
    # (He gets cut off by The Boss, as Brodie enters the office)"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b08
    tb"Shh! Brodie‚Äôs on his way in. Not a word about this until later, you got it?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b10
    lu"Yeah boss, I got it."
    # (Brodie approaches the meeting desk)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3bossmeeting b21
    with dissolve
    brod"Hey Dad, sorry I‚Äôm late."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b15
    tb"Looks like you had a rough night son. Is everything okay?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b22
    brod"Yeah I‚Äôm fine. I just had a bit of a late night out."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b16
    tb"I‚Äôll bet!"
    # (Brodie notices Lucas standing there, arms folded. He keeps this pose and standing position throughout the meeting)"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b26
    brod"Hang on, is that you Lucas?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b17
    lu"What up Brodie! Long time no see!"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b22
    brod"Dad, what‚Äôs going on? Why on earth is he here?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b16
    tb"I hired him. He‚Äôs just returned after being away for a few years and he works for me now."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b26
    brod"Why on earth would you hire this asshole? He was such a tool in high school."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b19
    lu"Hey! I‚Äôm standing right here ya know?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b20
    tb"Not that it‚Äôs any of your concern, but I owed Lucas' father a favour."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b14
    tb"It‚Äôs okay, Lucas will stay out of your way as long as you do your job."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b26
    brod"(What the hell is that supposed to mean? He makes it seem like Lucas is my own bodyguard.)"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b16
    tb"Speaking of which, I take it that all went well last night with that girlfriend of yours?"
    tb"Taking her to one of the most expensive restaurants in town, which I happen to own, should‚Äôve helped you to seal the deal, am I right?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b22
    brod"Yeah Dad, about that‚Ä¶"
    # (The Boss keeps talking, ignores Brodie)"
    # (The Boss stands and looks over the map of the lighthouse on the table)"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b27
    tb"Now that Brodie‚Äôs girlfriend has handed over the rights to the hotel to us, we can start making plans to finally demolish it."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b28
    tb"And once we‚Äôve done the same to the lighthouse, we can commence building a proper five-star hotel there."
    # (The Boss points to a section on the map)"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b27
    tb"I figure that we can put the pool and bar area over here, and maybe a recreation area on this side of the hotel grounds."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b31
    brod"Dad! [s_name] doesn‚Äôt want to sell the hotel!"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b29
    tb"SHE WHAT???"
    # (The Boss angry now)"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b31
    jump lb_day3_brodie_meeting_1

label lb_day3_brodie_meeting_1:
    brod"She said she‚Äôs going to turn the business around with the help of a close friend of hers who arrived from Darkham City earlier this week."
    brod"She‚Äôs not interested in selling or discussing it with me."

label lb_day3_brodie_meeting_2:
    brod"We got into a huge fight, even after I told her how much you were willing to offer her for it."
    brod"[s_name]‚Äôs not going to be enticed into selling because of money Dad. "
    show sc day3bossmeeting b30
