    lu"I suggest that you take a seat Brodie. The Boss is still talking to you."
    lu"(Little pipsqueak. He‚Äôs still just a spoilt rich-kid.)"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b32
    brod"Dad?? What the hell?"
    # (The Boss doesn‚Äôt look him in the eye)"
