    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3bossmeeting b33
    with dissolve
    tb"We‚Äôre doing things my way from now on. No more fucking around. Let me make this clear."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b34
    tb"I will destroy her and anyone who gets in my way. I don‚Äôt care who she is to you, do you hear me son?"
    show sc day1meetingbrodie b09
    brod"Yes Dad‚Ä¶"
    show sc day1meetingbrodie b15
