    mg"(Man, I sure have my work cut out‚Ä¶)"
    show sc day1meetingbrodie b10
    brod"Dad?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b33
    mg"I think the meeting is over Brodie. It‚Äôs probably best that you head off lad."
