label lb_day3_lucas_boss_chat:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 07 - Private chat between Brodie's father and Lucas"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (Brodie‚Äôs father remains with his back to Lucas)"
    scene sc day3bossmeeting b10
    with dissolve
    lu"What did you want to see me about boss?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b38
    tb"Don‚Äôt bullshit to me Lucas. What the hell happened this morning?"
    tb"And I want the truth."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b11
    lu"Just before I could lay down the law to [s_name], some girl came to her aid boss."
    lu"I have no idea who she was, but I didn‚Äôt want to cause a scene or draw too much attention to myself, so I left. "
    show sc day3bossmeeting b09
    tb"Do you think this girlfriend of Brodie‚Äôs knew who this person who helped her was?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b10
    lu"I think she was a complete stranger going by the way they were talking to each other."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b07
    tb"Well, at least you didn‚Äôt assault either of them."
    tb"Well done for keeping your cool, you‚Äôre already showing some signs of progress."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b38
    tb"But just remember that I pulled a lot of strings to keep you out of prison Lucas."
    tb"I also did your father a huge favour by hiring you, and I expect you to keep doing what I ask of you."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b12
    lu"I will boss, you have my word. "
    show sc day3bossmeeting b07
    tb"That‚Äôs great to hear. "
    show sc day3bossmeeting b13
    lu"So, do you want me to continue following [s_name]?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b09
    tb"No, forget her for now."
    tb"I want you to keep an eye on Brodie. I think he‚Äôs keeping something from me, I‚Äôm just not sure what yet."
    tb"He would‚Äôve gone home now, so just sit in your car outside his place and wait for him to leave."
    tb"If you see him do anything suspicious, then you let me know. You got it?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b12
    lu"Can do Boss."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b09
    tb"And before you leave, I want you to go and see Rudy downstairs."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b10
    lu"Huh? Why Rudy?"
    show sc day3bossmeeting b38
    tb"Because he‚Äôll provide you with a change of clothes."
    tb"I mean you're still wearing the same shit you had on three years ago before you left town Lucas!"
    tb"And if you‚Äôre going to work for me, you should at least look the part."
    show sc day3bossmeeting b39
    lu"All right fine, I‚Äôll go and see him."
    lu"(I think my clothes are fine the way they are, but whatever‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)



label lb_day3_s_comes_back:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 08 - Friend comes back to the living room and apologizes to MC"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (MC is waiting in the living room when Friend comes back)"
    scene sc day3schat s01
    with dissolve
    mc"(Okay, when [s_name] comes back, I have to try and keep my cool.)"
    mc"(Whatever happened between her and Brodie has clearly shaken her up, and she seems quite fragile at the moment.)"
    mc"(I need to hear her out and get all the details first before I respond or jump to any conclusions.)"
    mc"(And who exactly is this Jazmin girl?)"
    mc"(It seems odd that [s_name] would let some random person she met on the street, stay at her hotel for no good reason.)"
    scene sc day3schat s02
    mc"(And for free! I guess I‚Äôll find out who she is soon enough.)"
    # (friend returns, and has changed clothing)"
    scene sc day3schat s04
    s"Hey [y_name]. Sorry to keep you waiting."
    mc"It‚Äôs okay. Let‚Äôs have a seat, and talk about a few things, shall we?"
    scene sc day3schat s05
    s"Okay."
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (Friend and the Mc sit in the living room)"
    scene sc day3schat s15
    with dissolve
    mc"So uh, you were going to tell me what happened last night and why you didn‚Äôt return home until just now?"
    show sc day3schat s15
    s"I‚Äôll tell you everything [y_name] in a moment, but I just want you to know again how deeply sorry I am for last night‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3schat s13
    s"And for making you worry about me this morning. I feel really awful about it."
    # (Friend grabs MC‚Äôs hands)"
    show sc day3schat s15
    mc"I‚Äôm just relieved to see that you‚Äôre okay."
    mc"I was really worried about you [s_name], especially when I couldn‚Äôt get through to you."
    show sc day3schat s19
    s"I know, and I promise not to do that to you ever again."
    show sc day3schat s13
    mc"Why don‚Äôt you start from the very beginning, after you left here last night?"
    show sc day3schat s15
    s"Okay, well as you know, Brodie sent a car to come and pick me up."
    show sc day3schat s17
    s"I was pretty excited because we hadn‚Äôt seen each other in a few weeks."
    s"He wanted to see me because he said that he had figured out a way to resolve the issues with the hotel and the financial problems I‚Äôve been having as well."
    s"But things didn‚Äôt turn out the way I was expecting them to."
    mc"How come?"
    s"Brodie had just arrived back in town yesterday afternoon and he wanted to surprise me, because he wasn‚Äôt meant to return until next week."
    show sc day3schat s19
    s"I thought that he was going to look to personally invest in my hotel, but I was way off the mark with that one. It was worse than I thought."
    show sc day3schat s15
    mc"Okay, so why exactly did he want to see you then?"
    s"Well, I‚Äôll start from when I arrived at the restaurant to meet him‚Ä¶"


label lb_day3_flashback_s_brodie_night:
    scene sc day3sflashback f01
    with flash
    s"{i}Brodie greeted me when I arrived at the restaurant...{/i}"
    show sc day3sflashback f02
    s"{i}He told me how much he missed me, and he hoped that our night together would make up for his absence over the past few weeks.{/i}"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (Brodie and friend sit down for dinner)"
    show sc day3sflashback f03
    with dissolve
    s"{i}I later found out that his father owned the restaurant that we dined at last night.{/i}"
    show sc day3sflashback f04
    s"{i}Nevertheless, everything was going fine, that was up until we started talking about my hotel.{/i}"
    show sc day3sflashback f11
    brod"So anyway, aside from really wanting to see you [s_name], I have what I believe is an awesome proposition for you regarding your hotel."
    show sc day3sflashback f07
    s"Yeah, you were saying over the phone. So what‚Äôs the news you have for me?"
    # (Friend looks eager to hear it)"
    show sc day3sflashback f12
    brod"Look, I know how stressed out you‚Äôve been about it and how hard it‚Äôs been for you to try and run it by yourself‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3sflashback f11
    brod"But what if I told you that my Dad would be willing to give you a very generous offer to take it off of your hands."
    show sc day3sflashback f05
    s"Huh? You mean your Dad wants to buy my hotel off me?"
    show sc day3sflashback f11
    brod"Well yeah, that‚Äôs pretty much it. He could have an offer for you as soon as tomorrow morning."
    show sc day3sflashback f09
    s"I thought I already told you Brodie, I‚Äôm not going to sell the hotel for any amount of money."
    s"It‚Äôs all that I have and selling it would only prove that I failed as an owner."
    show sc day3sflashback f06
    s"Wait a minute‚Ä¶"
    s"Do you mean to tell me that this was the big news that you had to share with me?"
    show sc day3sflashback f13
    brod"I thought you‚Äôd be happy [s_name]."
    brod"I mean let‚Äôs be honest, things haven‚Äôt exactly been going well for you lately babe..."
    show sc day3sflashback f12
    brod"And it doesn‚Äôt look like anything is going to save the hotel from going under."
    show sc day3sflashback f06
    s"Well I beg to differ Brodie. I‚Äôve been in contact with a number of close friends who are going to help the hotel get back to its glory days."
    show sc day3sflashback f04
    s"They all work in industries that could be instrumental in changing the fortunes of my business. For the first time in ages, the outlook is pretty positive."
    jump lb_day3_flashback_s_brodie_night_1

label lb_day3_flashback_s_brodie_night_1:
