    brod"You know how powerful he is, and taking his offer seems like the smartest option here."
    show sc day3sflashback f06
    s"Well you can tell your Dad that I‚Äôm not interested. He‚Äôs just going to have to find somewhere else to spend his money."
    show sc day3sflashback f13
    brod"But [s_name]‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3sflashback f06
    s"No, I don‚Äôt want to talk about it anymore Brodie."
    show sc day3sflashback f09
    s"I came here to have a nice dinner with you because I missed you..."
