    show sc day3sflashback f17
    s"Huh? What did you just say to me?"
    # (Friend has an annoyed look on her face)"
    show sc day3sflashback f22
    brod"I uh‚Ä¶ All I said was-"
    # (Friend cuts him off)"
    show sc day3sflashback f23
    s"Dammit Brodie! I told you that I didn‚Äôt want to talk about it!"
    show sc day3sflashback f27
    brod"I know, but I just think-"
    # (Friend cuts him off)"
    show sc day3sflashback f29
    s"That‚Äôs the problem with you Brodie. You do too much thinking and not enough listening, to me especially!"
    s"I can‚Äôt believe you‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3sflashback f27
    brod"You can‚Äôt believe what exactly?"
    show sc day3sflashback f23
    s"This whole night, getting me to come out with you‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3sflashback f24
    s"It was never about wanting to see me, it was all about you trying to convince me to sell my hotel to your greedy father, wasn‚Äôt it?"
    show sc day3sflashback f25
    brod"You know that‚Äôs not true."
    # (Brodie doesn‚Äôt look her in the eye)"
    # (Friend starts to walk away)"
    s"Good night Brodie."
    show sc day3sflashback f29
    brod"Wait, where are you going?"
    s"I don‚Äôt know, home maybe? I just know that I can‚Äôt be anywhere near you right now."
    brod"Come on babe, don‚Äôt be like that."
    show sc day3sflashback f26
