    # (friend walks off)"
    show sc day3schat s10
    with flash
    mc"So you just walked away from him, just like that?"
    s"Yeah, the only problem was it was just after midnight and his place is a long walk from the hotel."
    s"I was going to call a taxi, but I then realised that the battery on my phone had died."
    s"So I had to walk."
    # (A shot of friend walking)"
    show sc day3schat s07
    mc"Did it take you all night to walk home?"
    show sc day3schat s10
    s"No, but after about half an hour my feet were getting tired from walking, and I happened to be near Victoria‚Äôs apartment block..."
    s"So I stopped by her place to see if she was home."
    # (A shot of friend outside Vicky‚Äôs house) "
