label lb_day3_flashback_vicky:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 10 - Flashback scene to Vicky's night out"
    # - friend waiting outside her place when she arrives home"
    # (Friend or the MC will narrate while friend tells the story. The narration part will be in brown italics)"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (Flashback scene CONTINUES)"
    scene sc day3sflashback f30
    with flash
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day3sflashback f30b","v_rewards_s_18")
    vic"[s_name], is that you?"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day3sflashback f35
    s"Victoria, hey..."
    show sc day3sflashback f32
    vic"Are you okay? It looks like you had a rough night!"
    show sc day3sflashback f35
    s"Yeah, I‚Äôm sorry to be here this late at night, but I was walking past your place and I couldn‚Äôt walk any further."
    show sc day3sflashback f33
    vic"What happened?"
    show sc day3sflashback f35
    s"I was with Brodie earlier tonight."
    show sc day3sflashback f34
    s"We had a fight and I walked out on him. It was only when I started to walk that I realised how far it was back to my hotel."
    s"And on top of that my phone battery died."
    show sc day3sflashback f35
    s"So I stopped here to see if you were home, and then I must have passed out."
    show sc day3sflashback f31
    vic"Well you‚Äôre lucky I was on my way home. I‚Äôve just been out with a few people myself."
    show sc day3sflashback f36
    s"Yeah I saw your post on your social media page."
    show sc day3sflashback f32
    vic"Did you want to crash at my place tonight?"
    show sc day3sflashback f35
    s"Yeah, if it‚Äôs no trouble? I can be gone before you wake up in the morning."
    show sc day3sflashback f31
    vic"You can leave whenever you want to girl."
    show sc day3sflashback f35
    s"Thanks Vicky, you‚Äôre a lifesaver!"
    # (Vicky helps friend walk into her place)"
    show sc day3schat s07
    with flash
    mc"So you stayed at Victoria‚Äôs last night?"
    s"Yes I did. She only has a small sofa so she offered to share her bed with me for the night."
    # (A shot of the girls in their underwear, sharing the bed)"
    mc"Oh! Did you fall asleep straight away?"
    s"Actually no, we stayed up talking for a while."
    show sc day3schat s10
    s"It turns out Vicky had been on a double-date earlier that evening, but much like my own date, it didn‚Äôt go very well."
    show sc day3schat s07
    mc"A date? With a guy?"
    s"Yeah, but they didn‚Äôt exactly hit it off. It was like a blind-date I think."
    # (Friend and Vicky face each other in the bed)"
    show sc day3sflashback f38
    with flash
    s"Your Dad would be so pissed if he found out you were on a date tonight Vicky!"
    show sc day3sflashback f43
    vic"I saw my Dad just before I went out."
    vic"I had to go over to the family home to grab my dress, and he came in just as I was about to leave."
    vic"He asked me if I was going on a date and I flat-out lied to him, telling my papi that I was going out with one of my girlfriends."
    show sc day3sflashback f42
    vic"I think he bought my excuse."
    show sc day3sflashback f43
    vic"But after how badly tonight went, I‚Äôm starting to wonder if my father is right about the guys that I‚Äôm interested in."
    show sc day3sflashback f38
    s"Don‚Äôt say that. They can‚Äôt all be perfect, just as I found out with Brodie!"
    show sc day3sflashback f41
    vic"Haha, I guess you‚Äôre right."
    show sc day3sflashback f42
    vic"I can‚Äôt help but feel a little depressed about being single and not having much time for a social life."
    show sc day3sflashback f43
    vic"The things I have to sacrifice just to have my own business‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3sflashback f43
    s"I hope what I‚Äôm about to say comes out right, because I‚Äôm more than a little drunk‚Ä¶"
    s"Anyway, I just wanted to tell you that I think you are one gorgeous woman Vicky..."
    s"And I‚Äôm sure that most guys would gladly walk in front of traffic just to have the chance to date you."
    # (Friend kisses her on the forehead)"
    show sc day3sflashback f44
    vic"Haha! Okay, just how much did you drink tonight [s_name]? Are you still drunk?"
    show sc day3sflashback f39
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3sflashback f39","sc day3sflashback f39x","v_pt_image_index_44")
    s"Haha, does a tree shit in the woods?"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc day3sflashback f44
    vic"Hahaha! You are so funny when you‚Äôve had a few too many drinks [s_name]."
    show sc day3sflashback f39
    s"Hey, I can hold my alcohol, don‚Äôt you worry!"
    show sc day3sflashback f45
    vic"Thanks [s_name], you sure know how to cheer me up. And at least we have each other, right?"
    # (Flashback scene ENDS, returns to friend and the MC on the sofa)"
    show sc day3schat s07
    with flash
    s"And that‚Äôs when I fell asleep. I don‚Äôt remember anything after that."
    mc"Do you remember what time you woke up?"
    s"Uh, yeah, it was around seven-thirty."
    # (show a shot of Vicky spooning friend)"
    show sc day3schat s08
    s"Vicky was still asleep, so I carefully snuck out of bed, got changed back into my dress, put my heels on and left her place."
    show sc day3schat s07
    s"I left Vicky a note before leaving, to say thanks and to let her know that I was heading home."
    mc"Okay, so you had a pretty rough night, but why were you so upset when you returned here this morning?"
    show sc day3schat s10
    s"The worst part of the past twelve hours happened not long after I left Vicky‚Äôs place."
    s"I had a bit of a headache and I suddenly found myself lost in town, not being able to work out how to get back to the hotel."
    show sc day3schat s11
    s"Then all of a sudden, I was confronted by this guy."
    mc"A guy? What guy?"
    show sc day3schat s10
    s"I don‚Äôt know who he was, but he seemed to know Brodie."
    mc"Did he hurt you?"
    show sc day3schat s11
    s"He scared me a little, and then he backed me against a wall."
    mc"(Son of a bitch!)"
    show sc day3schat s10
    s"I don‚Äôt know what would have happened if Jazmin wasn‚Äôt walking by, just as this guy confronted me."
    mc"What did she do?"
    s"Thankfully Jazmin intervened before anything could happen. But it was really strange [y_name]."
    s"This guy acted like he was trying to intimidate me, but then he backed off as soon as Jazmin told him to leave me alone."
    s"And then he walked off as though nothing had happened."
    mc"Did he say anything to you?"
    show sc day3schat s11
    s"Only that he‚Äôd be keeping an eye on me. It was really creepy."
    show sc day3schat s10
    mc"Geez‚Ä¶ But you‚Äôre definitely okay though?"
    s"Yes I am, but if not for Jazmin, I shudder to think what might have happened."
    mc"I‚Äôll bet. So that explains why you were happy to put Jazmin up for the night then? It makes perfect sense."
    show sc day3schat s08
    s"Yeah, she‚Äôs kind of my hero right now."
    show sc day3schat s07
    s"[y_name], I have a feeling the guy who confronted me was sent by Brodie, or maybe even his father."
    mc"I had the same feeling. Maybe he was sent to threaten or scare you because you didn‚Äôt agree to taking Brodie‚Äôs father‚Äôs offer."
    mc"If you know what‚Äôs best for you [s_name], I suggest that you stay away from Brodie for the time being."
    mc"At least until we can figure out who this guy who attacked you is and if Brodie‚Äôs father is involved somehow."
    mc"We also need to find out what he intends to do, now that you‚Äôve rejected his offer."
    mc"People like that don‚Äôt just walk away. I‚Äôve worked with and against people like that during my time in law."
    show sc day3schat s12
    s"[y_name], about what I said to you last night before I left here. I didn‚Äôt mean it and I‚Äôm sorry."
    s"You were right, and I should‚Äôve listened to you."
    # [I told you so / Calm response]"
    show sc day3schat s15
    menu:
        "I told you so":
            mc"Well, I hate to say I told you so [s_name]."
            mc"You shouldn‚Äôt have left me here by myself and you really need to consider changing your attitude and behaviour, otherwise I‚Äôll leave, for real this time."
            show sc day3schat s17
            s"Yeah, I know."
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,-1,s_name)
            mc"(I hate having to be hard on [s_name] but if I don‚Äôt tell her then no one is else is going to.)" #-1 Friend points."
            show sc day3schat s19
            s"And I really regret telling you that the hotel is mine alone. I‚Äôm just not used to working in a team, you know?"
            show sc day3schat s17
            s"But I promise that I will try and change."
            show sc day3schat s19
            s"I sometimes don‚Äôt make the right decisions, maybe it‚Äôs because I‚Äôm not as smart as you are [y_name]."
            s"I never finished college and I accept that I‚Äôm  not cut out for being a boss or a leader."
            show sc day3schat s15
            mc"I think you‚Äôre doing an okay job [s_name]."
            mc"You just need some guidance and a second persons opinion from time to time."
            mc"You have the right contacts I believe, and the best thing we can do is work with what we have for now, okay?"
            show sc day3schat s16
            s"Sounds good. Thanks for understanding [y_name]."
            s"And please don‚Äôt ever feel like you‚Äôre alone here in Sunshine Bay."
            s"I don‚Äôt want you to ever feel like that. You being here is very important to me."
        "Calm response"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc day3schat s15
            mc"It‚Äôs not your fault."
            mc"You thought you were doing the right thing and I guess I was feeling a little bit jealous because you have someone here and apart from you, I don‚Äôt really have anyone."
            mc"So for that I‚Äôm sorry too."
            # (they hug)"
            show sc day3schat s19
            s"I really regret telling you that the hotel is mine alone. I‚Äôm just not used to working in a team, you know?"
            show sc day3schat s17
            s"But I promise that I will try and change."
            s"I sometimes don‚Äôt make the right decisions, maybe it‚Äôs because I‚Äôm not as smart as you are [y_name]."
            s"I never finished college and I accept that I‚Äôm  not cut out for being a boss or a leader."
            show sc day3schat s15
            mc"I think you‚Äôre doing an okay job [s_name]."
            mc"You just need some guidance and a second persons opinion from time to time."
            mc"You have the right contacts I believe, and the best thing we can do is work with what we have for now, okay?"
            show sc day3schat s16
            s"Sounds good. Thanks for being so understanding [y_name]."
            s"And please don‚Äôt ever feel like you‚Äôre alone here in Sunshine Bay."
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,1,s_name)
            s"I don‚Äôt want you to ever feel like that. You being here is very important to me." # +2 Friend points."
    # (The MC smiles)"
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc day3schat s15
    mc"The main thing you need to know is that I want to be here, and I want to help out as best I can."
    show sc day3schat s16
    s"Well in that case, I‚Äôve made a decision."
    s"I want you to be the main person in charge when I‚Äôm not here."
    s"And from now on, we‚Äôre complete equals in the decisions we make regardless of who is involved or who we do business with."
    s"How does that sound?"
    mc"Oh, well thank you [s_name], but are you sure?"
    mc"I mean I still have a lot to learn about how to run a hotel, and very little time to do it."
    s"I‚Äôm sure you‚Äôll be fine and pick things up in no time."
    s"Like I said, you‚Äôre a pretty smart guy."
    s"And as for you being worried about not having anyone aside from yours truly..."
    s"I would fully support you making friends while you‚Äôre here in town, especially with the people you have met so far that are going to help us out with the hotel."
    show sc day3schat s18
    s"I mean they all seem to like you, especially The Twins!"
    show sc day3schat s16
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Have they been talking to [s_name] about me?)"
    mc"Okay great. Uh, I've organised for a few of your friends to drop by here today."
    mc"But is there anything that we should be doing now before they arrive?"
    show sc day3schat s05
    s"I‚Äôm just going to check on Jazmin real quick, to see if she needs anything."
    s"While I‚Äôm doing that, why don‚Äôt you go and check out the main kitchen area to familiarise yourself with it, before Victoria arrives here during her lunch break?"
    mc"Sure, I can do that."
    s"All right, I‚Äôll meet you in there shortly. And [y_name]?"
    mc"Yeah [s_name]."
    # (Friend kisses him on the cheek)"
    s"Thanks again, I really couldn‚Äôt do any of this without you..."
    mc"Oh, you‚Äôre welcome [s_name]."
    # (Friend smiles and then leaves the room)"
    mc"(I better check out this kitchen then‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)






label lb_day3_vicky_arrives_lunch:
    scene sc day3jazhotel h11
    with dissolve
    s"Hey Jazmin, it‚Äôs just me, [s_name]."
    show sc day3jazhotel h12
    jaz"I'm over here!"
    show sc day3jazhotel h07
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3jazhotel h07","sc day3jazhotel h07x","v_pt_image_index_45")
    jaz"Hey [s_name]."
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc day3jazhotel h04
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day3jazhotel h04b","v_rewards_s_19")
    s"I wanted to check to see if you needed anything?"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"I‚Äôm okay for now. I just had a quick look around the hotel. It‚Äôs pretty quiet."
    show sc day3jazhotel h01
    s"As I said, we‚Äôre going to officially re-open soon, plus we‚Äôve also closed down a wing of the hotel."
    show sc day3jazhotel h06
    jump lb_day3_vicky_arrives_lunch_1

label lb_day3_vicky_arrives_lunch_1:
    jaz"I see. So, how did the chat with your friend go?"

label lb_day3_vicky_arrives_lunch_2:
    show sc day3jazhotel h09
    jaz"I couldn‚Äôt help but notice that something is going on between you two."
    show sc day3jazhotel h01
    s"Huh? How do you mean?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"I mean it‚Äôs obvious that you two are close, but there‚Äôs evident friction too."
    jaz"And I take it you both have a lot of differences in opinion, correct?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h05
    s"Wow, is it that obvious?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"To me it was."
    show sc day3jazhotel h06
    jaz"But it‚Äôs not all bad though. It was also clear to see that deep down he cares about you too and he was worried something bad may have happened."
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"So what‚Äôs the story between you two?"
    jump lb_day3_vicky_arrives_lunch_3

label lb_day3_vicky_arrives_lunch_3:
    show sc day3jazhotel h03
    s"It‚Äôs kind of a long one."
    s"To cut the story quite short, my mother and I moved in with [y_name] and his father Gerald when I was nine years old."
    s"We all lived together for five or so years on a Navy base near where Gerald worked."
    s"But that was until my Mom and [y_name]‚Äôs father separated, and my mother took me back here to Sunshine Bay."
    s"Up until a few days ago, I hadn‚Äôt seen or spoken to [y_name] in almost nine years."

label lb_day3_vicky_arrives_lunch_4:
    show sc day3jazhotel h09
    jaz"Oh wow, it does sound like a pretty complicated story."
    show sc day3jazhotel h06
    jaz"But it‚Äôs great that you two were able to find each other again."
    show sc day3jazhotel h07
    jaz"I get the feeling there might be some significance in that."
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"So are you looking for people to help you make your hotel more attractive to guests and tourists?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h01
    s"Pretty much. Why do you ask?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h06
    jaz"Well when I was having a walk around earlier, I noticed that you have a health centre here, which is also currently closed."
    show sc day3jazhotel h01
    s"Yeah we do. The pool can still be accessed, but not the spa and exercise room."
    s"What did you want to know Jazmin?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"Well it‚Äôs clear to see that it‚Äôs in dire need of repairs. What I didn't mention to you earlier is the degree that I attained was in kinesiology."
    jaz"I‚Äôve also done some massage therapy and dabbled in beauty treatments as well."
    show sc day3jazhotel h02
    s"Oh, that‚Äôs surprising!"
    show sc day3jazhotel h07
    jaz"Yeah, it was a big reason why I wanted to stay at the other hotel, as I was hoping to check out their facilities and apply for a job there."
    show sc day3jazhotel h01
    s"Which hotel were you going to stay at Jazmin?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"It‚Äôs called Seascape Hotel."
    show sc day3jazhotel h05
    s"Oh‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"You know of it?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h03
    s"Yeah I do. It‚Äôs new in town, and it‚Äôs owned by my boyfriend‚Äôs father."
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"Oh wow! He must be worth a lot of money then."
    show sc day3jazhotel h03
    s"Yeah he is. And if I were to sell my hotel to him..."
    s"Then I‚Äôm almost certain he would look to knock this place down and put another high-rise like Seascape here in its place."
    show sc day3jazhotel h08
    jaz"And my guess is you don‚Äôt want to sell to him because it‚Äôs not about the money, correct?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h06
    jaz"You want to keep the hotel for your own personal pride and to prove to yourself that you can make this place a success."
    jaz"Am I right?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h02
    s"Yes, exactly!"
    show sc day3jazhotel h04
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3jazhotel h04","sc day3jazhotel h04x","v_pt_image_index_49")
    s"(It almost feels like Jazmin knows me better than I know myself!)"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc day3jazhotel h07
    jaz"I had a feeling. So because they allegedly lost my reservation, I found myself without a place to stay, therefore, I couldn‚Äôt apply for a job there either."
    jaz"So what I was thinking if you‚Äôre interested, that maybe I could help you and [y_name] fix up your health centre and run it for you?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h03
    s"Hmm‚Ä¶ I don‚Äôt know."
    show sc day3jazhotel h01
    s"I mean I like the idea, and eventually, we‚Äôre going to need someone to look after it once we get it up and running again."
    s"However, I‚Äôm going to need to discuss it with [y_name] first, before making a decision."
    show sc day3jazhotel h07
    jaz"Yes, of course, I understand completely."
    show sc day3jazhotel h06
    jaz"And if you‚Äôd like me to, I could forward you my credentials, a copy of my degree and resume to you as well?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h04
    s"That‚Äôd be awesome Jazmin."
    show sc day3jazhotel h01
    s"So uh, did you have any plans for the afternoon?"
    show sc day3jazhotel h07
    jaz"Well now that I‚Äôm here, I was thinking of taking a swim."
    jaz"I noticed that the pool is still in working order!"
    show sc day3jazhotel h04
    s"Haha, yeah it is."
    s"My onsite maintenance guy Mister Roshi cleans it every day, and he put some chlorine in the pool yesterday afternoon."
    s"So it should be all set for you to have a swim."
    show sc day3jazhotel h09
    jaz"I think I‚Äôll do that, as it‚Äôs been quite tiring for me ever since I arrived in town very early this morning."
    show sc day3jazhotel h06
    jaz"So I could do with an hour of just relaxing."
    show sc day3jazhotel h04
    s"All right, I‚Äôll leave you to it. I‚Äôm just going to be in the kitchen area of the restaurant if you need me for anything."
    s"You‚Äôll find some fresh towels on your way out to the pool area."
    show sc day3jazhotel h10
    jaz"Thanks [s_name]. I‚Äôll come and find you later."
    show sc day3jazhotel h04
    s"Have fun Jazmin."
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    jump lb_day3_vicky_arrives_final




label lb_day3_vicky_arrives_final:
    if _in_replay:
        if y_name == None:
            $ y_name = "MC"
        else:
            $ y_name = persistent.y_name

        if s_name == None:
            $ s_name = "S"
        else:
            $ s_name = persistent.s_name

        show screen toprightmenu

        play music "music/01/2936-fliegen-by-sascha-ende.mp3"
    scene sc day3vickitchen v01
    with dissolve
    mc"(Okay, Vicky should be here any minute now. I wonder what she‚Äôll be looking for when she arrives?.)"
    mc"(I mean it seems pretty professional looking to me, but what the hell would I know?)"
    # (Victoria arrives, calls out to the MC from behind)"
    if renpy.loadable("extras.animations") and persistent.v_anim_enabled:
        window hide
        scene wip_02_vic_kitchen  at tt_top
        pause
        window show
    else:
        show sc day3vickitchen v01
    vic"So, were you about to prepare some lunch for me [y_name]?"
    # (MC turns around - ROLLING WIP of Vicky)"
