label lb_day3_discussion_s_mc:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 12 - Discussion between Friend and the MC continues"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (scene continues after Vicky has left)"
    show sc day3vickitchen v43
    s"So, did you enjoy chatting with Vicky while I was gone?"
    # (Friend gives the MC a suspicious look)"
    mc"Uh, yeah. It was all right I guess."
    mc"(Is [s_name] insinuating something?)"
    show sc day3vickitchen v42
    s"Anyway, what did you think about her idea to open the restaurant to the public?"
    show sc day3vickitchen v43
    s"I was thinking that we could perhaps do some advertising that we can put out to the public, and maybe we could also get the Twins, Ivy and Lily to help us promote it."
    mc"That‚Äôs actually a pretty great idea!"
    mc"If done right, it could turn out to be good exposure for not only our business, but also Ivy and Lily‚Äôs."
    show sc day3vickitchen v42
    mc"And if the food served on the night is of a high quality, then it may be a huge benefit to Victoria‚Äôs business as well."
    s"So we could all potentially gain from having an event here at the hotel is what you‚Äôre saying?"
    mc"Yeah, possibly. There‚Äôs quite a lot of groundwork to be done first though."
    show sc day3vickitchen v43
    s"Of course."
    s"Okay, well I‚Äôll follow up with Victoria in the next day or two, and we can bring this up with the Twins when they stop by here this afternoon."
    show sc day3vickitchen v42
    s"There‚Äôs something else that I need to discuss with you [y_name]."
    s"I was just talking with Jazmin, and as it turns out, she has a degree in kinesiology."
    s"Plus she‚Äôs done a bit of beauty and massage therapy too."
    mc"All right, so what were you thinking?"
    s"I‚Äôm not sure if you‚Äôve noticed, but there‚Äôs a health centre here in the hotel. It‚Äôs just closed at the moment."
    s"So what I had in mind was to give Jazmin a job running it once we re-open it."
    s"I told her that I would discuss this with you first though."
    mc"Thank you, I‚Äôm glad that you did. Have you checked her credentials?"
    s"She‚Äôs going to forward them to me sometime today, which should include her references and resume."
    mc"That‚Äôs great [s_name]. However, a lot of it will depend on when it will be possible for us to re-open that part of the hotel."
    mc"Jazmin may not want to wait long if she‚Äôs looking for a job to start right away."
    show sc day3vickitchen v41
    s"Yeah, I did think about that."
    show sc day3vickitchen v42
    s"I‚Äôll let her know that working with us immediately may not be a guarantee, and that she might have to look for work elsewhere for the time being."
    mc"That‚Äôs probably a good idea. Is there anything else you need to discuss with me [s_name]?"
    show sc day3vickitchen v41
    s"Yeah, I was wondering if you could do me a huge favour [y_name]?"
    s"There are a few things that we need to set up in some of the hotel rooms that we painted, but Mister Roshi doesn‚Äôt have his main toolbox."
    mc"Okay, so where is it?"
    show sc day3vickitchen v42
    s"Well Randy, the guy who fell down the stairs in the lighthouse last week and broke his leg and both arms, he was the last person to have them."
    s"I need to run some errands and I was going to bring Jazmin along with me to show her around town..."
    s"So I was wondering if you would you be able to go over to Randy‚Äôs place to get them for me?"
    s"I can text you his address shortly."
    mc"Sure, whatever you need [s_name]."
    show sc day3vickitchen v44
    s"Thanks [y_name]."
    # (Friend hugs him and kisses him on the cheek)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/short_kiss_sound_effect.mp3"
    show sc day3vickitchen v45
    s"Mwah!"
    stop sound
    show sc day3vickitchen v43
    s"It finally feels like we‚Äôre getting somewhere, don‚Äôt you think?"
    mc"Yeah I agree. We got off to a slow start, but it does feel like the real work can start now."
    s"Okay, well I‚Äôll leave you to it and I‚Äôll meet you back here sometime this afternoon."
    s"Check your phone shortly for that message I'm going to send you, and then you can go get those tools when you‚Äôre ready."
    mc"Sounds good."
    s"Bye [y_name]."
    jump lb_day3_discussion_s_mc_1

