label lb_day3_randy_intro:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 13 - The MC goes to Randy‚Äôs house"
    # - The first introduction of Randy"
    # - I see Randy as someone in his mid to late 20s, a bit older than friend and the MC, short dark hair, funny looking"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (MC arrives at Randy‚Äôs house)"
    scene sc day3randyintro r01
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/03/01/Birds_in_trees_sounds_effects1.mp3" loop fadein 1.0
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ This must be the place. I wonder how this guy managed to fall down a flight of stairs?)"
    show sc day3randyintro r02
    mc"(I wonder what he‚Äôll be like?)"
    # (MC approaches the front door)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Door_Knock_Sound_Effect_Free.mp3"
    "(Knock, knock, knock)"
    stop sound
    #- sound effect to be added)"
    randy"JUST A SECOND!"
    # (he shouts from the other side of the door)"
    mc"(Okay, so just grab the box of tools, head back to the hotel, and then maybe I can have some lunch.)"
    # (Randy opens the door)"
    show sc day3randyintro r04
    randy"Oh hey, before you start, I‚Äôm not interested in donating Sir."
    show sc day3randyintro r08
    randy"As you can see, I‚Äôm off work at the moment."
    # (We see both of Randy‚Äôs arms and one of his legs in plaster)"
    show sc day3randyintro r09
    mc"Woah! That does look pretty bad!"
    show sc day3randyintro r04
    randy"Yeah it is. So anyway, maybe you can hit up the guy who lives down the road for some money, for whatever your cause is."
    show sc day3randyintro r07
    randy"He sits on his ass all day long and works maybe once a year, makes a shit-ton of money off a lot of people for doing next to nothing. Or so I‚Äôve heard."
    # (Randy looks to one side, not looking at the MC)"
    show sc day3randyintro r05
    mc"No no, I‚Äôm not here for any money. [s_name] sent me from the hotel."
    jump lb_day3_randy_intro_1

label lb_day3_randy_intro_1:
    mc"I‚Äôm a friend of hers, [y_name]."

label lb_day3_randy_intro_2:
    show sc day3randyintro r06
    randy"Oh fuck, sorry dude, I had no idea!"
    show sc day3randyintro r03
    randy"I thought you were another one of those fake charity guys!"
    mc"Haha, it‚Äôs cool. So it was a pretty nasty fall from what I was told."
    show sc day3randyintro r04
    randy"That‚Äôs one way to put it!"
    show sc day3randyintro r09
    randy"I broke my leg in two places..."
    show sc day3randyintro r08
    randy"Both arms were fractured, and I think I broke a bone in my ass. "
    show sc day3randyintro r04
    randy"Not that my doctor agreed with me."
    show sc day3randyintro r06
    randy"But it didn‚Äôt stop him from giving me one of those donut cushions, the bastard!"
    mc"(I‚Äôm not sure if I should laugh or not, haha.)"
    show sc day3randyintro r03
    mc"So uh, you don‚Äôt trust your doctor then?"
    randy"Nah he‚Äôs cool."
    randy"Although when I arrived at the hospital on the day that it happened, before I went into surgery, I said to the doc, ‚ÄúI think I broke my leg in two places.‚Äù"
    randy"Do you know what he replied to me?"
    show sc day3randyintro r06
    randy"‚ÄúWell you should probably stop visiting those places then!‚Äù"
    # (Randy smirks, looks to one side)"
    show sc day3randyintro r03
    randy"Smart ass‚Ä¶"
    mc"Hahaha! Yeah, that‚Äôs not the kind of advice you were probably looking for."
    mc"So anyway, [s_name] said that you were the last person to have a box of tools from the hotel and she asked if I could come and collect them from you."
    show sc day3randyintro r07
    randy"Right, about that. They‚Äôre not actually here dude."
    show sc day3randyintro r04
    randy"The day before my accident, I was asked if I could do a repair job at this local church, and because I wasn‚Äôt quite finished, I ended up leaving them there."
    show sc day3randyintro r09
    randy"And as you can see, I‚Äôm not exactly in the best condition to go and get them."
    show sc day3randyintro r06
    randy"Hey? Maybe you could go there and retrieve them?"
    show sc day3randyintro r03
    mc"Uh, sure but, do you think they will just hand them over to a complete stranger?"
    show sc day3randyintro r06
    randy"That‚Äôs not a problem at all! When you arrive, ask for a member of the church by the name of Kristina."
    show sc day3randyintro r03
    randy"Just mention my name and tell her that I sent you. She‚Äôll know where the tools have been stored."
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    mc"Okay, so is the church far from here?"
    randy"It‚Äôs about a ten-minute walk. Less than five minutes if you have a scooter."
    mc"Yeah, that‚Äôs not an option I‚Äôm afraid. I‚Äôll have to walk."
    mc"(Fuck! I really need to get myself one of these things.)"
    mc"(But that would mean having to learn how to ride one and being okay with it.)"
    show sc day3randyintro r04
    randy"Sorry I couldn‚Äôt be of any more help. How are you finding working at the hotel anyway?"
    show sc day3randyintro r05
    mc"It‚Äôs been okay so far."
    mc"There‚Äôs quite a bit to learn, but I‚Äôm sure I‚Äôll get the hang of it."
    show sc day3randyintro r06
    randy"You‚Äôll be fine. I mean what more could I guy ask for, hey? The beach, the sunshine, the girls!"
    show sc day3randyintro r08
    randy"It‚Äôs like paradise. Unless you‚Äôre a useless, temporarily crippled fuck like me!"
    show sc day3randyintro r03
    mc"Haha! Sorry to laugh Randy."
    randy"Nah it‚Äôs cool. Laughter is the best medicine for me at the moment, but only because I‚Äôm completely out of weed."
    randy"Anyway, is there anything else you need?"
    mc"No that should just about be it."
    mc"But I do have to ask, what does one do with their time when they have a broken leg and two broken arms?"
    show sc day3randyintro r04
    randy"Well shit, not much."
    show sc day3randyintro r03
    randy"I mean I‚Äôve considered writing a story based on my experience of falling down a flight of stairs though‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3randyintro r06
    randy"It‚Äôll be a step-by-step guide!"
    mc"Hahaha!"
    show sc day3randyintro r05
    randy"As you can see, I‚Äôm quite restricted by what I can and can‚Äôt do."
    show sc day3randyintro r04
    randy"Changing the TV channels can sometimes be quite tricky."
    randy"Going to the bathroom I can just about manage on my own, but jerking off is completely out of the question!"
    randy"So some of these online adult games that I‚Äôve been going through during my time off has been giving more than just blue balls, if you know what I mean!"
    show sc day3randyintro r05
    mc"Oh, I‚Äôm really sorry to hear that."
    mc"(Hahaha! I‚Äôm doing my best not to laugh out loud.)"
    show sc day3randyintro r10
    randy"Oh, just one thing before you get to the church [y_name]."
    show sc day3randyintro r04
    randy"Some of the members there are kinda crazy, especially the leader dude."
    randy"So try and avoid him at all costs, otherwise you might become one of them! Or a mindless zombie, who knows?"
    show sc day3randyintro r10
    mc"What about this Kristina girl though, is she one these crazies you speak of?"
    show sc day3randyintro r06
    randy"No she‚Äôs pretty solid, at least she has been every time I‚Äôve called in there."
    show sc day3randyintro r03
    randy"And she‚Äôs pretty easy on the eye too."
    randy"But you shouldn‚Äôt run into any issues with her."
    mc"Well that‚Äôs good to know. All right, well it was nice meeting you Randy."
    show sc day3randyintro r06
    randy"You too buddy. I‚Äôd shake your hand but, kind of a huge fucking problem right now."
    mc"Yeah, I understand."
    show sc day3randyintro r03
    randy"Oh, and before I forget, the place you‚Äôre looking for is the ‚ÄúFaith plus One‚Äù church."
    randy"Have fun dude!"
    # (Randy closes the door)"
    show sc day3randyintro r02
    mc"(Faith plus One? That‚Äôs the church that was mentioned on that sign that I saw in town the other day.)"
    mc"(Okay, well it looks like I‚Äôll get to see this place up-close for myself...)"
    mc"(And maybe find out if they‚Äôre the brain-washing group that some people in this town claim them to be.)"
    mc"(After what Randy just told me, I better tread carefully when I get there‚Ä¶)"
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0






label lb_day3_phone_call_cousin:
    show sc day3ccall c01
    play sound "sound effects/01/02/Tablet_ringing_sound_effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    mc"(Oh, someone is calling me.)"
    # [Answer it]"
    stop sound
    show sc day3ccall c03
    c"Hi [y_name], sorry to bother you, but is [s_name] with you?"
    show sc day3ccall c05
    c"I‚Äôve been trying to reach her but she‚Äôs not answering."
    mc"Hey [c_name]. Uh, no she isn‚Äôt with me."
    show sc day3ccall c03
    mc"I‚Äôm in the middle of running an errand for her because she‚Äôs quite busy today."
    c"Oh, well that probably explains why she‚Äôs not answering her phone."
    mc"Can I be of some assistance to you?"
    show sc day3ccall c06
    c"Uh, maybe you can."
    show sc day3ccall c03
    c"Do you remember my Mom, Trisha, who you met the other day?"
    mc"Yes of course."
    show sc day3ccall c06
    c"Okay, well she‚Äôs asked me to go somewhere to pick up some documents from a work colleague of hers..."
    c"But I don‚Äôt feel like I would be comfortable going there by myself."
    c"Would you mind coming over to my house and taking a short trip with me to this place?"
    show sc day3ccall c03
    mc"Yeah, sure I can! When were you thinking of going there?"
    show sc day3ccall c05
    c"As soon as possible. Where are you at the moment?"
    mc"I‚Äôve just left this guy Randy‚Äôs place. He was working with [s_name] before he hurt himself."
    show sc day3ccall c03
    c"Oh right, I heard about that. He fell down some stairs didn‚Äôt he?"
    mc"Yes he did. Do you know where he lives?"
    show sc day3ccall c02
    c"Yes I do, he‚Äôs not too far from here."
    c"So if you don‚Äôt have anywhere you need to be, would you be able to come over right now?"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I‚Äôve already told Randy that I‚Äôd be heading to the church, and he has a contact there who is expecting me.)"
    mc"(But this place that [c_name] wants me to go with her to sounds pretty important as well.)"
    mc"(Where should I go first?)"
    # [The Church / [c_name]‚Äôs house]"
    menu:
        "The Church"(wt="Favour Kristina"):
            $ v_day3_church_late = False
            $ v_day3_chouse_late = True
            show sc day3ccall c03
            mc"Uhh‚Ä¶ I might be a little late [c_name], as I promised [s_name] that I‚Äôd pick up these tools for her first."
            show sc day3ccall c05
            c"Okay sure, but please try and get here as soon as possible if you can. I‚Äôll send you through my address shortly."
            mc"Thanks, I‚Äôll do my best. Don‚Äôt worry, I‚Äôll definitely come over to see you."
            show sc day3ccall c02
            c"Thanks [y_name]. See you soon."
            mc"Bye [c_name]."
            # (call ends)"
            show sc day3randyintro r02
            mc"(All right, I better pick up this toolbox from the church as quickly as I can so I don‚Äôt keep [c_name] waiting.) "
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            jump lb_day3_kristina_intro


        "[c_name]‚Äôs house"(wt="Favour [c_name], Trisha, and Ashley"):
            $ v_day3_church_late = True
            $ v_day3_chouse_late = False
            show sc day3ccall c03
            mc"Uhh‚Ä¶ Sure I can [c_name], I‚Äôll come right over."
            show sc day3ccall c04
            c"Thank you so much [y_name]! I‚Äôll send you through my address shortly."    #1 COUSIN POINT
            show sc day3ccall c02
            mc"Great, I‚Äôll see you soon."
            c"Bye [y_name]."
            # (call ends) "
            show sc day3randyintro r02
            mc"(All right, I better go and help sort out this problem [c_name] has as quickly as possible, so I don‚Äôt keep this girl at the church waiting.) "
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            jump lb_day3_trisha_intro






label lb_day3_trisha_intro:

    scene sc day3trishahouse t01
    with dissolve
    mc"(Much like Ashley‚Äôs house, this is a pretty nice looking place too.)"
    mc"(I wonder what kind of work Trisha does for a living?)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Door_Knock_Sound_Effect_Free.mp3" fadein 1.0
    "(Knock, knock, knock)" #- Door Knock - sound effect to be added"
    stop sound fadeout 1.0
    show sc day3trishahouse t01
    tri"Hey there. Can I help you?"
    mc"Hi Trisha. It‚Äôs me, [y_name]. We met the other day near the beach."
    if renpy.loadable("extras.animations") and persistent.v_anim_enabled:
        window hide
        scene wip_02_trisha_intro  at tt_top
        pause
        window show
    else:
        show sc day3trishahouse t02
    jump lb_day3_trisha_intro_1

label lb_day3_trisha_intro_1:
    tri"Oh right, of course. You're [s_name]‚Äôs friend."

label lb_day3_trisha_intro_2:
    show sc day3trishahouse t03
    tri"What brings you here?"
    mc"Uh, [c_name] called and asked if I could help her out with something."
    show sc day3trishahouse t02
    tri"Oh, I see. Sorry, she never mentioned this to me. But please, come on in."
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (The MC sits down with Trisha in the living room. Trisha, unlike Ashley who was laying across the sofa, sits in a recliner, legs crossed)"
    scene sc day3trishahouse t08
    with dissolve
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3trishahouse t08","sc day3trishahouse t08x","v_pt_image_index_53")
    tri"Don‚Äôt mind [c_name], she‚Äôll be out shortly."
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day3trishahouse t09b","v_rewards_trisha_1")
    tri"So, how have you found your first few days in Sunshine Bay?"
    mc"It‚Äôs been okay so far. A lot to take in, but I‚Äôm managing."
    tri"Yes, fixing a hotel from scratch is always going to be a huge challenge no matter what the circumstances are."
    show sc day3trishahouse t09
    tri"But I‚Äôm sure you have your own plans and ideas on how to make the place great again, am I right?"
    mc"Uh, yeah I guess so."
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    tri"You come from a law background if I understand it correctly?"
    mc"Yes I do. How did you know that?"
    show sc day3trishahouse t09
    tri"I have my sources. I like to take interest in those that work closely with any of my family members you see."
    tri"Plus I asked my sister Ashley about you."
    mc"Oh, so those are your sources then."
    show sc day3trishahouse t13
    tri"Haha, you caught me out counsellor."
    # (Trisha holds her hands up and smiles)"
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    mc"Well, I was never that kind of lawyer, unfortunately."
    mc"I‚Äôve had about seven years studying and working in the field of law, but it hasn‚Äôt quite worked out the way I hoped it would."
    show sc day3trishahouse t09
    tri"Maybe you just needed a new experience, and Sunshine Bay is the best place for a person to unleash their adventurous side."
    tri"Tell me [y_name], do you consider yourself an adventurous type of guy?"
    # (Trisha gives the MC an alluring look here, maybe leans forward, shows some cleavage unintentionally)"
    # [Yes I am / I‚Äôm not too sure]"
    menu:
        "Yes I am"(wt="Best choice"):
            mc"Yeah, I believe that I am, or at least I‚Äôm trying to be."
            tri"Well coming all the way down here to Sunshine Bay is a good start."
            tri"I know this town inside out, I know where all the hot spots are and where most people go for a good time."
            tri"I‚Äôd sure like to show you a good time while you‚Äôre here for the summer [y_name]."
            tri"So if you ever need someone to show you some new experiences, then please, give me a call."
            $ trisha_points = change_stat(trisha_points,2,"Trisha")
            mc"Oh, well that sure would be nice Trisha. I may just take you up on that offer." #+2 Trisha Pts"
        "I‚Äôm not too sure":
            show sc day3trishahouse t10
            mc"I‚Äôm not sure to be honest."
            mc"Several years of living in a miserable city, on top of studying and working in law since the age of eighteen, adventurous isn‚Äôt exactly a word I‚Äôd use to describe my life up until this point."
            show sc day3trishahouse t09
            tri"Well you‚Äôre young, and you still have the whole summer ahead of you to see the best of what this place has to offer."
            tri"I know this town inside out, I know where all the hot spots are and where most people go for a good time."
            tri"I‚Äôd sure like to show you a good time while you‚Äôre here for the summer [y_name]."
            tri"So if you ever need someone to show you some new experiences, then please, give me a call."
            mc"Oh, well that sure would be nice Trisha."
            # (scene continues)"
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    tri"So you‚Äôre happy to go with [c_name] to get these documents for me?"
    mc"Yeah, I just happened to be in the area when she called me."
    show sc day3trishahouse t12
    tri"And you also know she suffers from social anxiety, correct?"
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    mc"So I‚Äôve recently discovered, yes."
    show sc day3trishahouse t11
    tri"I wanted [c_name] to go to this gentleman‚Äôs place by herself but she insisted upon calling someone to go with her."
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    tri"I just had no idea that she called you."
    tri"Is there any reason why she would ask for you specifically?"
    mc"Oh, I think I might know why."
    mc"I‚Äôve been trying to help [c_name] with her problems in making conversation with other people."
    mc"We had a short session together yesterday and she did pretty well."
    show sc day3trishahouse t09
    tri"Well I‚Äôm glad to hear that she‚Äôs trying to do something about that."
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    tri"I‚Äôm someone who communicates with a lot of members of the public on a daily basis, so having a socially awkward daughter isn‚Äôt exactly a good look."
    show sc day3trishahouse t09
    tri"But it‚Äôs really great to know that you‚Äôre trying to help her open up and change. I appreciate it very much." #+2 Trisha Pts"
    mc"You‚Äôre welcome. I like to help people where I can you know?"
    jump lb_day3_trisha_intro_3

label lb_day3_trisha_intro_3:
    tri"Clearly. I mean, you came all this way to help [s_name], and now you‚Äôre doing the same for [c_name]. I admire that."

label lb_day3_trisha_intro_4:
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    mc"So if you don‚Äôt mind me asking Trisha, what is it that you do for a living?"
    show sc day3trishahouse t09
    tri"I‚Äôm the head assistant to the mayor of Sunshine Bay."
    tri"I also act as his PR consultant, and I run errands for him if it‚Äôs required."
    mc"It sounds like quite a busy profession then?"
    show sc day3trishahouse t13
    tri"Oh yeah, it‚Äôs a godsend if I ever get the chance to put my feet up for a few minutes!"
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    mc"So this place that you want us to get your documents from, is there anything we need to know about it?"
    tri"Uh no, not really."
    tri"Norman, the guy who is holding them for me can be a bit of a grumpy old man, and he also has a vicious guard dog."
    show sc day3trishahouse t09
    tri"But that shouldn‚Äôt be an issue for you both as he usually ties him down in the backyard in the morning, and lets him run free in the afternoon."
    show sc day3trishahouse t10
    mc"Well that‚Äôs a relief, especially because I suffer from a mild case of Cynophobia."
    tri"Oh, you don‚Äôt like dogs being around you?"
    mc"Small dogs I‚Äôm usually okay with. The bigger ones, not so much."
    show sc day3trishahouse t09
    tri"Oh, well it‚Äôs just as well you‚Äôre going to see Norman now, rather than later."
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day3trishahouse t14
    tri"Hang on a second, I‚Äôll just go and get [c_name] for you. Wait right here."
    tri"(Where is that girl??)"
    # (Trisha gets up to find cousin)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    # (Trisha stands outside Cousins bedroom door)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3trishahouse t19
    with dissolve
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day3trishahouse t19b","v_rewards_trisha_2")
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Door_Knock_Sound_Effect_Free.mp3" fadein 1.0
    "(Knock, knock, knock)"
    #- Door Knock - sound effect to be added"
    stop sound fadeout 1.0
    tri"[c_name]? [y_name] is here. What are you doing in there?"
    c"Tell him I‚Äôll be out in a couple of minutes Mom!"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3trishahouse t15
    with dissolve
    tri"She‚Äôll be out soon [y_name]. Anyway, I have to be heading back to the office."
    show sc day3trishahouse t16
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3trishahouse t16","sc day3trishahouse t16x","v_pt_image_index_54")
    tri"Let‚Äôs catch up again real soon, yes?"
    mc"Sure, that would be nice Trisha."
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    # (The MC stands before Trisha)"
    # [Shake her hand / Kiss her on the cheek / Say goodbye]"
    menu:
        "Shake her hand":
            #‚Äù -1 Trisha Pt"
            $ trisha_points = change_stat(trisha_points,-1,"Trisha")
            # (MC does this action, Trisha gives him an indifferent look)"
            show sc day3trishahouse t28
            tri"Uh, I‚Äôll see you later [y_name]."
        "Kiss her on the cheek"(wt="Best choice"):
            #+1 Trisha Pt"
            $ trisha_points = change_stat(trisha_points,1,"Trisha")
            play sound "sound effects/01/02/Male_kissing_girl_on_the_cheek.mp3"
            # (MC does this action, Trisha gives him a surprised look)"
            stop sound
            show sc day3trishahouse t29
            tri"(Oooh, I like his confidence.)"
        "Say goodbye":
            #-1 Trisha Pt"
            $ trisha_points = change_stat(trisha_points,-1,"Trisha")
            # (Go down to the next line beneath)"
            # (scene continues)"
            show sc day3trishahouse t16
            mc"Bye Trisha."
    show sc day3trishahouse t16
    tri"Oh, before I go."
    show sc day3trishahouse t30
    tri"Drop me a line any time you‚Äôd like to catch up."
    # (Trisha hands it to the MC)"
    show sc day3trishahouse t31
    mc"Oh, thanks Trisha."
    show sc day3trishahouse t32
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day3trishahouse t32b","v_rewards_trisha_3")
    mc"(I‚Äôll make sure to store Trisha‚Äôs number into my tablet, and then I could perhaps give her a call tomorrow some time.)"
    $ v_char_trisha_known = True
    $ renpy.notify("Trisha has been added to the Relationship Menu.")
    tri"Bye [y_name]."
    # (she walks off towards the front door, looking over at her shoulder at the MC with a mischievous smile)"
    # (Trisha leaves)"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day3trishahouse t33
    mc"(Damn‚Ä¶)"
    # ROLLING WIP OF COUSIN"
    if renpy.loadable("extras.animations") and persistent.v_anim_enabled:
        window hide
        scene wip_02_c_house  at tt_top
        pause
        window show
    else:
        show sc day3trishahouse t26
    c"Hey [y_name]."
    show sc day3trishahouse t26
    c"Sorry, I was just working on something online for my course."
    show sc day3trishahouse t27
    $ c_points = change_stat(c_points,3,c_name)
    c"Thanks again for coming at such short notice." #+1 Cousin Pts (for being early)"
    mc"Oh, it‚Äôs no problem at all."
    show sc day3trishahouse t24
    c"Is my Mom still here?"
    mc"No uh, she just left."
    show sc day3trishahouse t25
    c"Great. Just give me a few minutes and then we can go and get this thing for my Mom."
    show sc day3trishahouse t27
