    scene sc day3trishahouse t34
    with dissolve
    mc"(Wow, this is a really nice house. It looks like both sisters did very well for themselves.)"
    # (Cousin comes out of her room)"
    show sc day3trishahouse t27
    c"Okay, I‚Äôm ready to go now."
    show sc day3trishahouse t24
    mc"Sweet. Say, is Trisha here? I‚Äôd love to be able to say hello to her."
    show sc day3trishahouse t26
    c"No, she left about half an hour ago, as she was required back at the office."
    show sc day3trishahouse t24
    $ v_char_trisha_known = True
    $ renpy.notify("Trisha has been added to the Relationship Menu.")
    mc"If you don‚Äôt mind me asking, what does your Mom do for a living?"
    show sc day3trishahouse t27
    c"She‚Äôs the head assistant to the mayor of Sunshine Bay. She also acts as his PR consultant and sometimes runs errands for him if it‚Äôs required."
    mc"It sounds like quite a busy profession then?"
    c"Oh yeah, during the day my Mom is rarely home."
    show sc day3trishahouse t24
    c"She received a phone call earlier on from this guy Norman who told her that these documents she had ordered had arrived."
    c"But then she was called back into the office by the mayor shortly after."
    c"So as you can see, one thing took precedence over the other."
    mc"Which is why she asked you to go and pick them up?"
    show sc day3trishahouse t26
    c"Yeah, exactly."
    show sc day3trishahouse t24
    mc"Do you think you could give me her number [c_name]?"
    mc"With everything going on with the hotel at the moment..."
    mc"There‚Äôs a few things that I‚Äôd like to ask your Mom that I think she might be able to answer, given the esteemed position that she‚Äôs in, working closely with the mayor."
    show sc day3trishahouse t27
    c"Uh, sure I can [y_name]."
    show sc day3trishahouse t35
    c"She always leaves some business cards here in case people come to the house while she is out, and if they urgently need to get in contact with her. "
    # (Cousin hands the MC the business card)"
    mc"Thanks for that."
    show sc day3trishahouse t27
    mc"(I‚Äôll make sure to store Trisha‚Äôs number into my tablet, and then I could perhaps give her a call tomorrow some time.)"
    c"Anyway, let‚Äôs head over to this guys place now so we have these documents for when my Mom returns home."
    mc"No problem."
    show sc day3trishahouse t36
    mc"Uh, do you mind if I leave this toolbox here so I don‚Äôt have to carry it with me?"
    show sc day3trishahouse t37
    mc"I‚Äôll come and collect it after we‚Äôve been to this guy‚Äôs house."
    show sc day3trishahouse t38
    c"Sure, that‚Äôd be fine."
    mc"Thanks [c_name]."
    #(MC puts the toolbox down on the floor)"
