label lb_day3_cousin_document:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 16 - MC and Cousin go to pick up and important document"
    # - two versions of this scene - if the player arrives here first or second"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # IF THE PLAYER GOES TO COUSIN + TRISHA‚ÄôS FIRST"
    # (scene begins with the MC and cousin standing outside the old man, Norman‚Äôs house - maybe a front fence so we see the yard but not the dog)"
    scene sc day3doghouse d01
    with dissolve
    play sound "sound effects/01/03/Morning Sound Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    mc"Is this the place?"
    c"According to my Mom‚Äôs details it should be."
    show sc day3doghouse d02
    mc"Did Trisha say exactly what these documents were for?"
    show sc day3doghouse d05
    c"No she didn‚Äôt. But she was very insistent on me getting them for her today."
    show sc day3doghouse d02
    mc"Okay, well let‚Äôs make sure we get them for her."
    show sc day3doghouse d06
    c"(I don‚Äôt know why, but I‚Äôm not as nervous as I normally would be in this situation.)"
    c"(It‚Äôs probably because [y_name] is with me.)"
    stop sound fadeout 1.0
    # (Cousin presses on the door bell)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (Ding Dong!) - Door Bell - sound effect to be added"
    scene sc day3doghouse d23
    with dissolve
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Door_Knock_Sound_Effect_Free.mp3" fadein 1.0
    "(Knock, knock, knock)"
    stop sound fadeout 1.0
    # (Norman answers the door, several locks are unlocked here)  Multiple unlocking sounds here - sound effect to be added"
    mc"(It sounds like his front door is more secure than the Darkham City bank vault!)"
    show sc day3doghouse d21
    norm"Yeah, what do you two want?"
    play sound "sound effects/01/03/Morning Sound Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    show sc day3doghouse d13
    c"Uh‚Ä¶"
    c"(Okay, now I‚Äôm worried. Why does this always happen?)"
    show sc day3doghouse d21
    mc"(I better answer for [c_name].)"
    show sc day3doghouse d15
    mc"Good morning Sir."
    mc"We‚Äôre here to pick up some documents for a lady named Trisha."
    show sc day3doghouse d13
    mc"This is her daughter [c_name]."
    show sc day3doghouse d16
    norm"You‚Äôre going to have to be a bit more specific."
    show sc day3doghouse d22
    norm"I have several various documents scattered on my dining table that are still yet to be collected."
    show sc day3doghouse d15
    mc"Trisha works for the mayor, and she‚Äôs sent us to pick up some important documents for her."
    show sc day3doghouse d16
    norm"Hmm‚Ä¶ Well, she didn‚Äôt tell me that someone would be coming over to collect them on her behalf."
    norm"And the deal I made with Trisha is that we would make the exchange in person and that she pays the rest of the finders fee."
    show sc day3doghouse d15
    mc"Fee? How much does she owe?"
    show sc day3doghouse d16
    norm"Two hundred dollars. So if you two were to cough up the money for her, I‚Äôll give you those documents."
    norm"Otherwise, get the hell off my property, as I need to take a shower and head into town!"
    # (Cousin turns to the MC)"
    show sc day3doghouse d09
    c"[y_name], I don‚Äôt have that kind of money."
    show sc day3doghouse d15
    mc"Thank you for your time Sir."
    stop sound
    show sc day3doghouse d16
    norm"Grr‚Ä¶ Kids‚Ä¶"
    play sound "sound effects/01/03/Door Slam - sound effect.mp3"
    show sc day3doghouse d23
    with vpunch
    mc"Ohh!"
    stop sound
    # (Norman slams the door shut) Door Slam - sound effect to be added"
    show sc day3doghouse d09
    c"What are we going to do now [y_name]?"
    c"I promised my Mom that we would get those documents for her by the time she returned home from work."
    mc"Well we could always call Trisha and tell her that this guy wants his money."
    show sc day3doghouse d08
    c"Oh, I guess we could do that."
    mc"Or‚Ä¶ Hang on, I‚Äôve got an idea for how we could maybe get them now, but I‚Äôm going to need your help."
    show sc day3doghouse d12
    c"Uh, okay. What‚Äôs your plan?"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (Cousin and the MC stand outside the yard fence. IMPORTANT: Add a sign on the fence that says ‚ÄúBeware of the DOG‚Äù)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/03/Morning Sound Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    scene sc day3doghouse d30
    with dissolve
    c"What are we doing outside the old man‚Äôs yard for [y_name]?"
    show sc day3doghouse d29
    mc"Well, if he‚Äôs not going to give us those documents, then I‚Äôm going to break in and get them."
    show sc day3doghouse d29
    c"Oh my god! Are you serious?? What if you get caught?"
    show sc day3doghouse d34
    c"And how will you even know where to find those documents inside the house?"
    show sc day3doghouse d30
    mc"Simple. The old man said that the documents are on a dining table inside his home."
    mc"Plus he said that he‚Äôs about to go for a shower."
    mc"So that probably gives me five, maybe ten minutes maximum."
    show sc day3doghouse d25
    mc"(Hopefully he‚Äôs left one of the side doors unlocked.)"
    show sc day3doghouse d34
    c"Uh, [y_name]? One problem..."
    show sc day3doghouse d24
    c"He has a guard dog."
    # (Cousin points to the sign on the outside of the fence)"
