    show sc day3doghouse d27
    mc"Give me one second [c_name], I‚Äôm just going to check something."
    # (MC looks over the fence, and sees the dog tied up)"
    show sc day3doghouse d42
    mc"Okay, it looks like I‚Äôm good to go. The dog is there, but he‚Äôs tied down."
    mc"And if he starts barking, then that means I‚Äôm going to have to be really quick!"
    show sc day3doghouse d34
    c"Please be careful [y_name]."
    show sc day3doghouse d27
    mc"I‚Äôll be fine."
    show sc day3doghouse d28
    mc"(It‚Äôs just as well that dog is restricted from moving, otherwise, there‚Äôd be no way in hell I‚Äôd be doing this!)"
    show sc day3doghouse d30
    mc"[c_name], if I signal to you, then you‚Äôre going to have to distract the old man somehow."
    c"Huh? How?"
    mc"Get him to answer the front door."
    mc"I may need to come back out through the yard, so you‚Äôre going to have to help me."
    show sc day3doghouse d34
    c"Okay, I‚Äôll try."
    show sc day3doghouse d29
    mc"Hopefully it doesn‚Äôt come to that. All right, I‚Äôm going in‚Ä¶"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (The MC is in the backyard)"
    scene sc day3doghouse d69
    with dissolve
    mc"(Okay, so the side door to the house is only a few yards away.)"
    # (MC looks around)"
    show sc day3doghouse d42
    mc"(It looks like he‚Äôs asleep...)"
    stop sound fadeout 1.0
    show sc day3doghouse d37
    mc"(So I better tip-toe carefully, because even the slightest noise might wake him up.)"
    # (MC stands on the dogs‚Äô squeaky chew toys) Squeaky noise - sound effect to be added"
