            # (MC gets to the door, opens it)"
            show sc day3doghouse d41
            mc"(Right, I won‚Äôt have much time until the old man finishes his shower. I better move quickly.)"
    # [Go to the living room]"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (The MC is now in the living room, overlooking a work table that has numerous sheets of paper, documents, parcels, it‚Äôs a huge mess)"
