label lb_day3_cousin_document_late:
    # IF THE PLAYER GOES TO COUSIN + TRISHA‚ÄôS PLACE SECOND"
    # (scene begins with the MC and cousin walking and talking)"
    scene sc day3doghouse d05
    with dissolve
    play sound "sound effects/01/03/Morning Sound Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    c"So why were you late [y_name]?"
    show sc day3doghouse d02
    mc"I ran into some problems at the church trying to get the toolbox back for [s_name]."
    mc"I was expecting it to be easy, but it was far from it."
    show sc day3doghouse d05
    c"Which church did you have to go to?"
    show sc day3doghouse d02
    mc"Uh, Faith plus One."
    show sc day3doghouse d04
    c"Oh, now I understand why you took so long."
    mc"You‚Äôve heard of them?"
    c"Yeah, I‚Äôve seen them around town. They didn‚Äôt try and convert you, did they?"
    mc"Haha, I‚Äôm not sure, maybe?"
    show sc day3doghouse d02
    mc"But it‚Äôs okay, I‚Äôm not one part of their church now if that‚Äôs what you‚Äôre worried about."
    show sc day3doghouse d03
    c"Haha!"
    # (scene begins with the MC standing outside the old man, Norman‚Äôs house - maybe a front fence so we see the yard but not the dog)"
    show sc day3doghouse d01
    mc"Is this the place?"
    c"According to my Mom‚Äôs details it should be."
    show sc day3doghouse d02
    mc"Did Trisha say exactly what these documents were for?"
    show sc day3doghouse d05
    c"No she didn‚Äôt. But she was very insistent on me getting them for her today."
    show sc day3doghouse d01
    mc"Okay, well let‚Äôs make sure we get them for her."
    show sc day3doghouse d06
    c"(I don‚Äôt know why, but I‚Äôm not as nervous as I normally would be in this situation.)"
    c"(It‚Äôs probably because [y_name] is with me.)"
    stop sound fadeout 1.0
    # (Cousin presses on the door bell)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3doghouse d23
    with dissolve
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Door_Knock_Sound_Effect_Free.mp3" fadein 1.0
    "(Knock, knock, knock)" #- Door Bell - sound effect to be added"
    stop sound fadeout 1.0
    play ambient "sound effects/01/03/Morning Sound Effect.mp3" loop fadein 1.0
    # (Norman answers the door, several locks are unlocked here)  Multiple unlocking sounds here - sound effect to be added"
    mc"(It sounds like his front door is more secure than the Darkham City bank vault!)"
    show sc day3doghouse d16
    norm"Yeah, what do you two want?"
    show sc day3doghouse d13
    c"Uh‚Ä¶"
    c"(Okay, now I‚Äôm worried. Why does this always happen?)"
    show sc day3doghouse d21
    mc"(I better answer for [c_name].)"
    show sc day3doghouse d15
    mc"Good morning Sir. We‚Äôre here to pick up some documents for a lady named Trisha."
    mc"This is her daughter [c_name]."
    show sc day3doghouse d16
    norm"You‚Äôre going to have to be a bit more specific."
    norm"I have quite a number of documents scattered on my dining table that are still yet to be collected."
    show sc day3doghouse d15
    mc"Trisha works for the mayor, and she‚Äôs sent us to pick up some important documents for her."
    show sc day3doghouse d22
    norm"Hmm‚Ä¶ Well, she didn‚Äôt tell me that someone would be coming over to collect them on her behalf."
    norm"And the deal I made with Trisha is that we would make the exchange in person and that she pays the rest of the finders fee."
    show sc day3doghouse d13
    c"Fee? How much does she owe?"
    show sc day3doghouse d22
    norm"Two hundred dollars. So if you two were to cough up the money for her, I‚Äôll give you those documents."
    norm"Otherwise, get the hell off my property, as I need to take a shower and head into town! "
    # (Cousin turns to the MC)"
    show sc day3doghouse d09
    c"[y_name], I don‚Äôt have that kind of money."
    show sc day3doghouse d15
    mc"Thank you for your time Sir."
    show sc day3doghouse d16
    norm"Grr‚Ä¶ Kids‚Ä¶"
    play sound "sound effects/01/03/Door Slam - sound effect.mp3"
    show sc day3doghouse d23
    with vpunch
    mc"Oh!"
    stop sound
    # (Norman slams the door shut) Door Slam - sound effect to be added"
    show sc day3doghouse d09
    c"What are we going to do now [y_name]?"
    c"I promised my Mom that we would get those documents for her by the time she returned home from work."
    mc"Well we could always call Trisha and tell her that this guy wants his money."
    c"Oh, I guess we could do that."
    show sc day3doghouse d08
    mc"Or‚Ä¶ Hang on, I‚Äôve got an idea for how we could maybe get them now, but I‚Äôm going to need your help."
    c"Uh, okay. What‚Äôs your plan?"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (Cousin and the MC stand outside the yard fence. IMPORTANT: Add a sign on the fence that says ‚ÄúBeware of the DOG‚Äù)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/03/Morning Sound Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    scene sc day3doghouse d29
    with dissolve
    c"What are we doing outside the old man‚Äôs yard for [y_name]?"
    show sc day3doghouse d30
    mc"Well, if he‚Äôs not going to give us those documents, then I‚Äôm going to break in and get them."
    show sc day3doghouse d29
    c"Oh my god! Are you serious?? What if you get caught?"
    c"And how will you even know where to find those documents inside the house?"
    show sc day3doghouse d27
    mc"Simple. The old man said that the documents are on a dining table inside his home."
    mc"Plus he said that he‚Äôs about to go for a shower."
    mc"So that probably gives me five, maybe ten minutes maximum."
    show sc day3doghouse d25
    mc"(Hopefully he‚Äôs left one of the side doors unlocked.)"
    show sc day3doghouse d34
    c"Uh, [y_name]? One problem. He has a guard dog."
    # (Cousin points to the sign on the outside of the fence)"
    show sc day3doghouse d24
    mc"(Oh fuck‚Ä¶)"
    show sc day3doghouse d28
    mc"Give me one second [c_name], I‚Äôm just going to check something."
    # (MC looks over the fence, and sees the dog laying down, but not tied up)"
    show sc day3doghouse d103
    mc"(I must be insane to even try this, considering how much I dislike big dogs.)"
    # (Should I take the risk or not?)"
    # [Don‚Äôt risk it / Risk it]"
    show sc day3doghouse d30
    menu:
        "Don‚Äôt risk it":
            mc"Dammit, his dog isn‚Äôt tied down, so there goes that idea."
            show sc day3doghouse d29
            c"So, what are we going to do?"
            show sc day3doghouse d30
            mc"Well I don‚Äôt have two hundred dollars on me."
            $ trisha_points = change_stat(trisha_points,-3,"Trisha")
            mc"I‚Äôm afraid you‚Äôre going to have to tell your Mom what happened here." #-3 TRISHA POINTS"
            show sc day3doghouse d34
            c"Yeah, I think you‚Äôre right. Thanks for coming with me and trying to help."
            show sc day3doghouse d29
            mc"You‚Äôre welcome, although I wish I could‚Äôve done more."
            show sc day3doghouse d34
            $ c_points = change_stat(c_points,-3,c_name)
            c"It's okay..."
            show sc day3doghouse d29
            mc"Oh, I still need to pick my tools from your house."
            c"Yes, of course. Let‚Äôs head back there now‚Ä¶"
            stop sound fadeout 1.0
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            #(cousin and the MC outside her house)"
            scene sc day3trishahouse t26
            with dissolve
            c"Well, you have your things."
            mc"Thanks [c_name]."
            mc"And again, I‚Äôm really sorry we couldn‚Äôt get those documents for your Mom.."
            c"It‚Äôs okay, I‚Äôll take care of it."
            c"Well, goodbye for now [y_name]. We‚Äôll talk again soon."
            mc"Bye [c_name]."
            #(C leaves)"
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            scene sc day3trishahouse t01
            with dissolve
            mc"(Dammit. I really let her down.)"
            mc"(But there‚Äôs no way I could gather up the courage to try and get past that big ugly mutt in there.)"
            mc"(I better get back to the hotel as [s_name] could already be waiting for me to return.)"
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            jump lb_day3_mc_walks_back





        "Risk it"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc day3doghouse d30
            mc"Dammit, his dog isn‚Äôt tied down, so there goes that idea."
            c"So, what are we going to do?"
            # (MC looks around)"
            mc"If I play this smart, I think I can get into the house."
            show sc day3doghouse d29
            c"Are you serious??"
            mc"Yeah, I have to at least try."
            mc"And if he starts barking, then that means I may have to jump back over this fence real quick!"
            show sc day3doghouse d34
            c"Please be careful [y_name]."
            show sc day3doghouse d27
            mc"I‚Äôll be fine."
            show sc day3doghouse d28
            mc"(Oh my god, this is insane. What the hell am I thinking??)"
            show sc day3doghouse d30
            mc"[c_name], if I signal to you, then you might have to distract the old man somehow."
            c"Huh? How?"
            mc"Get him to answer the front door. I may need to come back out through the yard, so you‚Äôre going to have to help me."
            show sc day3doghouse d34
            c"Okay, I‚Äôll try."
            mc"Hopefully it doesn‚Äôt come to that. All right, I‚Äôm going in‚Ä¶"
            stop sound fadeout 1.0
            # (screen goes blank)"
            # (The MC is in the backyard)"
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            scene sc day3doghouse d69
            with dissolve
            play sound "sound effects/01/03/Morning Sound Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
            mc"(Okay, so the side door to the house is only a few yards away.)"
            # (MC looks around)"
            show sc day3doghouse d103
            mc"(It looks like he‚Äôs asleep...)"
            show sc day3doghouse d38
            mc"(So I better tip-toe carefully, because even the slightest noise might wake him up.)"
            show sc day3doghouse d119
            mc"(Which way should I move?)"
            window hide
            call screen scr_minigame_dog
            show screen scr_minigame_clock
            $ v_minigame_clock = 0
            # [Behind the tree / Stay against the wall]"
            menu:
                "Behind the tree"(wt="Best choice"):
                    # (MC stands behind the tree)"
                    show sc day3doghouse d116
                    mc"(Okay, he hasn‚Äôt seen me‚Ä¶ Yet.)"
                    stop sound
                    show sc day3doghouse d122
                    mc"(All right, I‚Äôm almost there. Now to step forward, and‚Ä¶)"
                    # (MC stands on the dog‚Äôs squeaky chew toys) Squeaky noise - sound effect to be added"
                    play sound "sound effects/01/03/Squeaky noise - sound effect.mp3"
                    mc"(Uh-oh!)"
                    stop sound
                    # (Dog turns and sees the MC)"
                    # (Dog starts barking) - Dog Barking - sound effect to be added"
                    play sound "sound effects/01/03/Large Dog Barking Sound Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
                    show sc day3doghouse d123
                    mc"(Oh crap! What do I do now??)"
                    menu:
                        "Run for the house":
                            show sc day3doghouse d124
                            mc"(Shit! I better make a beeline for the house!)"
                            stop sound fadeout 1.0
                            # (Dog continues barking during the scene) - Dog Barking - sound effect continuously running here"
                            # (MC gets to the door, opens it)"
                            scene black
                            with dissolve
                            scene black
                            with Pause (2)
                            scene sc day3doghouse d61
                            with dissolve
                            $ v_minigame_clock += 1
                            play sound "sound effects/01/03/Large Dog Barking Sound Effect Lower.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
                            mc"(Thank god the door was open, but now the dog won‚Äôt stop barking!)"
                            mc"(Well I won‚Äôt have much time until the old man hears him and works out that something isn‚Äôt right. I better move quickly.)"
                            stop sound fadeout 1.0
                            # [Go to the living room]"
                            # (screen goes blank)"
                        "Throw the toy at the dog"(wt="Best choice"):
                            $ v_day3_doghouse_dogtoy = True
