                            mc"(Thank god the door was open, but now the dog won‚Äôt stop barking!)"
                            mc"(Well I won‚Äôt have much time until the old man hears him and works out that something isn‚Äôt right. I better move quickly.)"
                            stop sound fadeout 1.0
                        "Throw the toy at the dog"(wt="Best choice"):
                            #‚Äù (NOTE: The toy could look like a pork chop)"
                            $ v_day3_doghouse_dogtoy = True
                            show sc day3doghouse d40
                            mc"(Oh god I hope this works‚Ä¶ )"
                            show sc day3doghouse d44
                            stop sound
                            mc"(Phew! That should hopefully shut him up for a while.)"
                            show sc day3doghouse d41
                            mc"(Okay, let‚Äôs see if the door is unlocked.)"
                            mc"(Right, I won‚Äôt have much time until the old man finishes his shower. I better move quickly.)"
                            scene black
                            with dissolve
                            scene black
                            with Pause (2)
                            scene sc day3doghouse d46
                            with dissolve


    show sc day3doghouse d46
    mc"(Shit! Those documents of Trisha‚Äôs could be anywhere on here.)"
    show sc day3doghouse d58
