            jump lb_day3_church_menu
            # *NOTE: Once the options come back up, ‚ÄúCheck the desk drawer again‚Äù will be there instead. There will be a secret compartment under the draw."
            # i.e. [Behind the picture frame / Check the desk drawer again / Under the pot plant]"

        "Check the desk drawer again" if v_day3_church_drawer:
            # [Behind the picture frame / Check the desk drawer again / Under the pot plant]"
            show sc day3church c55
            mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Maybe I should check the desk drawer again?)"
            # (MC opens the drawer)"
            show sc day3church c70
