            mc"(This must be it!)"
            mc"(I wonder if this is where [k_name] thought the key was when she left me the instructions that I lost?)"
            # (*There will be some photos that are also in the draw that will be upside-down. The player must click on them for the MC to view them)"
            # ‚ÄúIf the player clicks on the photos‚Äù"
            show sc day3church c59
            mc"(Oh, I wonder what this is?)"
            # (MC turns them over, sees a priest with a couple of strippers)"
            show sc day3church c69
