                k"Even though I‚Äôve expressed my desire to change things around here, they‚Äôre very intent on keeping the same look for now."
                jump lb_day3_kristina_intro_late_menu
            mc"(We've already talked about this.)"
            jump lb_day3_kristina_intro_late_menu

label lb_day3_kristina_intro_late_menu_end:
