    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day3yukiswimstore s45
    with dissolve
    mc"I can‚Äôt thank you enough for the lift Yuki. If not for you I‚Äôd still be walking up that hill!"
    yuki"Yeah, it‚Äôs good to work out your legs, but not if you didn‚Äôt have that in mind."
    mc"Haha‚Ä¶"
    show sc day3yukiswimstore s46
