        "Quiet":
            show sc day3twinhall t23
            mc"Uh‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs really quiet?"
            show sc day3twinhall t25
            ivy"True, but not exactly what I would have said."
            show sc day3twinhall t26
            ivy"It has a lot of promise, possibilities, potential."
            show sc day3twinhall t27
            ivy"When Lily and I look at a function room for the first time..."
            show sc day3twinhall t33
            ivy"We look at every section, every corner, every little bit of detail for how we can turn an ordinary-looking room like this one, into a real party atmosphere that attendees will never forget."
        "It has potential"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc day3twinhall t23
