            show sc day3twinhall t27
            ivy"When Lily and I look at a function room for the first time, we look at every section..."
            show sc day3twinhall t33
            ivy"Every corner, every little bit of detail for how we can turn an ordinary-looking room like this one, into a real party atmosphere that attendees will never forget." #. +1 TWINS PT"
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc day3twinhall t26
