    ivy"Oh yeah, loads of it."
    show sc day3twinhall t33
    ivy"When I close my eyes and then re-open them, I can see plenty of tables with people sitting or standing around them."
    ivy"There‚Äôs people on the dance floor or queuing up at the bar, plenty of waiters and waitresses working, pouring champagne, a band would be playing up on a platform stage, streamers, balloons, banners, the works!"
    ivy"Can you see it?"
