    show sc day3twinhall t38
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3twinhall t38","sc day3twinhall t38x","v_pt_image_index_69")
    mc"There‚Äôs a bar area we‚Äôve set up for the night, dance lights, a DJ booth and they‚Äôve requested a specific colour theme for the lighting and balloons."
    mc"Maybe it‚Äôs a birthday, maybe it‚Äôs a wedding reception. Whatever the event is, it‚Äôs a pretty big deal."
    # (MC opens his eyes, the room is empty again)"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc day3twinhall t36
    mc"How was that?"
    ivy"Not bad. Not bad at all."
    show sc day3twinhall t24
    ivy"I see you were paying attention when you came to visit me and Lily yesterday at our office."
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    mc"I find that it‚Äôs always important to give others in business your full attention."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    mc"So, is this room ready to start hosting events then Ivy?"
    show sc day3twinhall t28
    ivy"It‚Äôs okay, but it still needs some work."
    ivy"What you guys really could do with is an interior designer..."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    ivy"And have them change this room so when people come to see it for the first time, they will immediately consider hiring it as soon as they set foot in here."
    ivy"It doesn‚Äôt have to be overly flashy, just nice enough for people with various budgets to want to book this events room."
    mc"Do you know anyone like that?"
    ivy"Not someone professionally, no. How about you?"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I wonder if that girl [k_name] I met earlier today knows enough about this kind of thing?)"
    mc"No. Well, not anyone here in Sunshine Bay."
    mc"Besides, like you and your sister, I haven‚Äôt been in town long enough to build my own clients list."
    mc"And I don‚Äôt think [s_name] knows anyone like that either, but I could check with her."
    show sc day3twinhall t25
    ivy"It would be best if you get that fixed, sooner rather than later."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    ivy"This wedding function that Lily and I were assigned to earlier today to coordinate is at a local resort."
    ivy"And the hosts have offered their guests the option to stay at the resort hotel that night, as an option."
    ivy"It‚Äôs set for not this weekend, but the weekend after."
    ivy"So that‚Äôs something to keep in mind when booking events here in the future."
    mc"How did that function come about on such short notice?"
    ivy"Another business similar to ours decided to drop out due to the workload and through fear of not having everything ready in time."
    ivy"Inside information tells us that they‚Äôve gone bankrupt and the people that they hired to work at the wedding wanted the money upfront."
    show sc day3twinhall t24
    ivy"The option to step in was offered to us through a friend who is attending the wedding, and naturally we jumped at the chance!"
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    mc"That‚Äôs really cool. I‚Äôd sure love to see you and Lily in action."
    ivy"Well Lily and I had been discussing the idea of inviting you and [s_name] to come to one of our events when you have a night free."
    ivy"Would you be interested?"
    mc"Definitely! What kind of event did you have in mind?"
    ivy"We have a few different parties coming up that have been booked in."
    ivy"It‚Äôs not as big of a deal as a wedding, but they're still pretty important events, and you‚Äôll be able to see the detail and time it takes for us to set up a party room for these kinds of occasions."
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    ivy"Tell me [y_name], are you engaged?"
    mc"(Woah‚Ä¶ That question came out of the blue!)"
    mc"No, I‚Äôm not."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    ivy"But you‚Äôve been with your partner for, five years is it?"
    mc"Yes I have. How did you know that?"
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    ivy"I hope you don‚Äôt mind, we asked [s_name] a bit about you earlier on."
    ivy"We wanted to get an idea of your position on relationships and your experiences when it comes to being engaged, married, or in a long-term relationship."
    ivy"It‚Äôs the kind of thing us girls sometimes talk about you see."
    ivy"It would seem that your experience is limited when it comes to the first two, but that‚Äôs okay."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    mc"What about you Ivy? I don‚Äôt see a ring on your finger, or Lily‚Äôs."
    mc"So, are either of you dating anyone?"
    show sc day3twinhall t24
    ivy"Why so interested [y_name]?"
    # (she gives a sexy smirk to the obvious flirting)"
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    mc"No reason."
    mc"I just figured you wanted to know so much about me, so I felt it was only right that I ask you a personal question too."
    ivy"Hmm‚Ä¶ Fair enough."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    ivy"Lily and I are so busy with our business that dating isn‚Äôt exactly high on our agendas."
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    ivy"But that‚Äôs not to say that we don‚Äôt like to have the odd fling with a guy every once in a while."
    ivy"We just make it clear to them that we‚Äôre not looking for anything serious."
    ivy"Most guys that we meet or hook up with seem to be more than okay with that."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    mc"I see. So you‚Äôre both just playing the field I guess?"
    ivy"More or less. Did you have any other questions that you would like to ask me, regarding our business specifically?"
    mc"(It feels like she wants to get off the topic of dating and relationships.)"
    mc"I just had one more question about the design of this events room Ivy."
    mc"Can someone studying interior design be capable of turning this room into the kind of place that would be appealing to all types of people looking to hold a function here?"
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    ivy"Well yeah, of course. And it‚Äôs a good way to save on money as well by hiring a knowledgable college student."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    ivy"Did you have someone in mind?"
    mc"Yeah I do. I met this girl from the local church who could possibly be an ideal addition, especially if it means us saving some money on costs."
    show sc day3twinhall t25
    ivy"Hang on‚Ä¶ Did you just say that you went to a church today?"
    mc"Yeah I did. How come?"
    ivy"Which church did you go to?"
    mc"It‚Äôs called Faith plus One."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    ivy"Oh, so you‚Äôve met [k_name] I take it?"
    mc"Yeah I did. You know her?"
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    ivy"She‚Äôs our little sister."
    mc"Oh wow, for real?"
    ivy"For real."
    show sc day3twinhall t24
    ivy"Not only that, but the minister of the church is also our father."
    show sc day3twinhall t24
    with vpunch
    if v_day3_church_toolbox_open:
        #‚ÄúIf the player chose ‚ÄúOpen it‚Äù (the toolbox) during the Kristina church scene, the MC will already know this‚Äù
        mc"(Oh! So [k_name] really did say that he‚Äôs her father. And he‚Äôs also Ivy and Lily‚Äôs Dad too!)"
        mc"He‚Äôs your Dad??  Wow, I never would have guessed."
    else:
        #‚ÄúIf the player chose ‚ÄúDon‚Äôt open it‚Äù (the toolbox) during the Kristina church scene, the MC will not know this‚Äù
        mc"He‚Äôs your Dad??  Wow, I never would have guessed."
        # (scene continues)"
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    ivy"Yeah, not a lot of people are aware of this, mainly because he doesn‚Äôt approve of our lifestyles and the work that Lily and I do."
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    ivy"And [k_name], well she‚Äôs always been a Daddy‚Äôs girl, but that‚Äôs not to say that she‚Äôs completely innocent."
    mc"Huh? How do you mean?"
    ivy"She may appear to be committed to the church, but she‚Äôs really no different to me and Lily."
    ivy"There‚Äôs a party girl in her that is dying to get out, she just hasn‚Äôt realised it yet."
    mc"Nah, I don‚Äôt believe you, not after speaking to her this morning."
    ivy"You‚Äôll see. You may not believe it now city boy, but in time you will."
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs hard to tell if Ivy is telling the truth about her younger sister or just having me on.)"
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    mc"So, do you think we should hire [k_name]?"
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    ivy"Yeah I think you should."
    ivy"Not only would you get someone who has been obsessed with decorating and design from a young age..."
    ivy"But maybe you could be the one to persuade her into leaving the church."
    show sc day3twinhall t23
    ivy"Lily and I have tried so many times with [k_name], but she simply refuses to, probably out of fear of disappointing dear old Daddy."
    mc"(Surely that‚Äôs her choice, but I can‚Äôt say that to Ivy, as I don‚Äôt want to get into an argument with her over something that‚Äôs obviously a family issue.)"
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    ivy"Say, what are you doing tomorrow night?"
    mc"I don‚Äôt think I have any plans. What did you have in mind?"
    ivy"I‚Äôd like to invite you and [s_name] to have dinner with me and Lily."
    ivy"We can go through some room designs and further plans for this hotel that we have in mind."
    ivy"Plus it would give us a chance to get to know you better. And it feels like you need a night out to party with some real women."
    # (Ivy moves in close to the MC)"
    show sc day3twinhall t24
    ivy"So, what do you say?"
    # [I‚Äôm in / I‚Äôll think about it]"
    show sc day3twinhall t26
    menu:
        "I‚Äôm in"(wt="Favour Lily and Ivy"):
            $ v_day3_twins_imin = True
            show sc day3twinhall t26
            mc"Sure, count us in."
            $ tw_points = change_stat(tw_points,2,"Lily and Ivy")
            show sc day3twinhall t24
            ivy"Excellent. I‚Äôll give you a call sometime tomorrow to let you know of a time and place."
            show sc day3twinhall t26
            mc"Great."
            mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Hopefully [s_name] won‚Äôt mind if we do something with Ivy and Lily without me checking with her first.)" #+2 TWINS PTS, -2 FRIEND PTS"
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,-2,s_name)
        "I‚Äôll think about it"(wt="Favour [s_name]"):
            $ v_day3_twins_imin = False
            show sc day3twinhall t23
            mc"Uh, I‚Äôll get back to you on that Ivy."
            mc"[s_name] and I have quite a bit to do here and having a night out may not be ideal at this point in time."
            mc"I‚Äôm not saying no, but I‚Äôll have to see if it can be done."
            show sc day3twinhall t26
            ivy"Sure, I understand. I‚Äôll give you a call sometime tomorrow to see if you‚Äôre both interested‚Ä¶"
            mc"Thanks."
            mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I should check with [s_name] first to see if she‚Äôd be okay with us doing something with Ivy and Lily.)"
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,1,s_name)
            mc"(I'm sure she'd be okay with it, but it's better to run it by her first...)" # +1 FRIEND PT"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (Lily and friend return)"
    scene sc day3twinhall t01
    with dissolve
    s"Hey you two, did you learn much from Ivy [y_name]?"
    show sc day3twinhall t04
    mc"Oh yeah, plenty enough for now. How did you two go?"
    show sc day3twinhall t19
    lily"Very well [y_name]."
    lily"You‚Äôve done amazingly well to organise the office to make it easy for anyone who works in there, and to navigate their way through all the paperwork and supplies."
    lily"So great job!"
    mc"Thanks. Being organised is something I‚Äôm a little OCD with."
    show sc day3twinhall t29
    ivy"Anyway, Lily and I have to get going."
    ivy"We have a long night of planning ahead for this function that we‚Äôre hosting this weekend."
    show sc day3twinhall t05
    s"Please, allow me to walk you two out."
    # (Lily hugs the MC)"
    show sc day3twinhall t42
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/short_kiss_sound_effect.mp3"
    lily"Mwah!"
    stop sound
    show sc day3twinhall t19
    lily"Bye [y_name]. You guys are doing superb work here. Keep it up!"
    # (Lily kisses the MC on the cheek)"
    mc"Oh, thanks Lily."
    # (Lily talks with friend while Ivy and the MC embrace)"
    # (Ivy hugs the MC)"
    show sc day3twinhall t12
    ivy"Thanks for spending some time discussing ideas and information with me [y_name]. It‚Äôs greatly appreciated."
    mc"Likewise Ivy. It was definitely interesting."
    # (Ivy kisses the MC on the cheek, then whispers in his ear)"
    show sc day3twinhall t39
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/short_kiss_sound_effect.mp3"
    ivy"Mwah!"
    stop sound
    show sc day3twinhall t40
    ivy"I really hope we do get to see you tomorrow night. We can have all kinds of fun together‚Ä¶"
    # (Lily and friend don‚Äôt see this)"
    show sc day3twinhall t41
    mc"(Oh!)"
    ivy"Speak to you soon [y_name]."
    # (Ivy has a straight-faced look here, as though nothing happened)"
    show sc day3twinhall t09
    mc"(What was all that about??)"
    show sc day3twinhall t04
    s"I‚Äôll just walk Ivy and Lily back to their car [y_name]. I‚Äôll see you inside in a few minutes."
    mc"Sure thing [s_name], I‚Äôll be in the kitchen."
    show sc day3twinhall t09
    mc"Goodbye ladies."
    "Bye [y_name]."
    # (they walk out with friend)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)


label lb_day3_nicole_tablet:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 20 - MC's talks to Nicole on the tablet"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (MC sits in the kitchen)"
    scene sc day3evekitchen k01
    with dissolve
    mc"(That sure was an interesting talk with Ivy.)"
    mc"(I wonder exactly what she meant by the three of us having fun tomorrow night?)"
    mc"(I know that the sisters have offered to help try and attract more people to the hotel with their business, but I have to also remain focused on the job at hand‚Ä¶)"
    mc"(Even if the temptation to have a night out and let loose in Sunshine Bay seems really appealing.)"
    mc"(Then again, tomorrow could be like mixing business with pleasure, or something like that.)"
    # (Friend enters the kitchen)"
    show sc day3evekitchen k03
    s"Hey‚Ä¶"
    mc"Hey [s_name]."
    show sc day3evekitchen k05
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3evekitchen k05","sc day3evekitchen k05x","v_pt_image_index_70")
    s"So I‚Äôd say it was a pretty successful end to the day, don‚Äôt you think?"
    mc"Yes I would. And I‚Äôm confident that it won‚Äôt be long before this place hosts its first major event."
    s"You sound so self-assured about that."
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc day3evekitchen k03
    mc"I‚Äôm only going by whatever has been put before me, and I do feel like we‚Äôre on the right track and we have some talented and well-educated people helping us."
    show sc day3evekitchen k04
    s"I think you‚Äôre right. So as I said to you earlier, I‚Äôd like to make dinner for you [y_name]."
    show sc day3evekitchen k05
    mc"Would you like some help with that? Maybe we could make it together?"
    s"Okay, that would be really nice."
    # (Friend approaches the MC)"
    show sc day3evekitchen k08
    s"And if I forget to say it later, thanks for your help today [y_name]."
    show sc day3evekitchen k05
    s"Thanks for getting the tools, for being concerned with me after what happened this morning, and for discussing some ideas with Ivy just now."
    s"I know for sure I couldn‚Äôt do any of this without you, and I know I keep saying this, but I‚Äôm so happy that you‚Äôre here."
    mc"Hey, that‚Äôs why you asked me to come down, right?"
    show sc day3evekitchen k04
    s"Yeah, it is."
    # (Friend smiles)"
    show sc day3evekitchen k06
    s"Okay, well let‚Äôs get a start on dinner then, shall we?"
    s"There should be plenty of food in the fridge for us to make something to more than whet our appetites‚Ä¶"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (scene restarts with the MC and friend working alongside each other in the kitchen)"
    # (The MC could be cooking food like strips of chicken in a frying pan while friend is cutting up some vegetables)"
    scene sc day3evekitchen k09
    with dissolve
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3evekitchen k09","sc day3evekitchen k09x","v_pt_image_index_71")
    s"That smells really good over there [y_name]. I‚Äôm just about ready to add these veggies too."
    mc"Great. I think a nice Beaujolais will go well with dinner."
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc day3evekitchen k12
    s"I agree, maybe you‚Äôd like to-"
    # (Friend gets cuts off by a phone call on his tablet) Tablet_Ringing_Sound_Effect.mp3 to be added here"
    play sound "sound effects/01/02/Tablet_ringing_sound_effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    show sc day3evekitchen k10
    s"Oh! I think someone is trying to call you on your tablet."
    # (MC picks it up and sees Nicole‚Äôs profile on there)"
    mc"It‚Äôs okay, it's Nicole. She doesn‚Äôt normally ring this early, so it must be important."
    show sc day3evekitchen k09
    s"You can answer it in the other room if you‚Äôd like? I can watch the food."
    show sc day3evekitchen k10
    mc"Before I do, maybe you could say hello to her."
    show sc day3evekitchen k09
    s"Oh, I guess I could do that. It would be nice to speak to her for the first time."
    mc"All right, hang on a second."
    # [Answer it]"
    stop sound
    # (Nicole‚Äôs face pops up on screen)"
    show sc day3evekitchen k15
    mc"Hey Nicky."
    nic"Hey baby, how are you doing?"
    mc"I‚Äôm doing really well thanks. You?"
    show sc day3evekitchen k16
    nic"Pretty good too. I had another long day in court and now I‚Äôm just having a glass of wine before I go to bed."
    show sc day3evekitchen k14
    nic"Where are you at the moment?"
    mc"I‚Äôm just in the kitchen making some dinner, and uh, there‚Äôs someone here that would like to say hello to you too."
    # (Friend enters the screen for Nicole to see her)"
    show sc day3evekitchen k21
    s"Hi Nicole, it‚Äôs nice to finally meet you."
    show sc day3evekitchen k18
    nic"Oh, hi [s_name]. Um, how are you?"
    # (Nicole is a bit surprised that friend is there with the MC)"
