    nic"She seems nice. And you two seem like you‚Äôre getting on pretty well."
    show sc day3evekitchen k25
    mc"It hasn‚Äôt been all smooth sailing as you know..."
    mc"But we made some great progress today, and I feel like I‚Äôm starting to find my footing here in this town."
    show sc day3evekitchen k26
    nic"That‚Äôs great [y_name], I‚Äôm really happy for you."
    show sc day3evekitchen k25
    mc"Forgive me, but, I thought that you were going to call me a bit later? Or I was going to call you."
    show sc day3evekitchen k24
    nic"Yeah, I‚Äôm sorry about that."
    nic"I have a really early start tomorrow morning and a ton of research to go through tonight."
    nic"So I‚Äôm afraid we won‚Äôt be able to‚Ä¶ Well, you know?"
    mc"Oh, right‚Ä¶"
    nic"Yeah, my apologies for the change in plans, and for interrupting your dinner."
    show sc day3evekitchen k25
    mc"It‚Äôs okay, you weren‚Äôt to know."
