    show sc day3evekitchen k26
    nic"I‚Äôm glad it‚Äôs all going well for you there [y_name], and that you‚Äôre getting along with [s_name]."
    mc"Thanks."
    show sc day3evekitchen k26
    nic"Anyway, I thought I‚Äôd give you a quick call to tell you that I love you, and I was thinking that maybe we can speak in the next day or two?"
    show sc day3evekitchen k27
