label lb_day3_s_night_in:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 21 - MC and Friend have a nice night in"
    # - drink wine, discuss the future, end the night on a good note"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (scene returns from his call with Nicole, friend has dinner ready for him on the table, and the bottle of wine)"
    scene sc day3hoteldinner d09
    with dissolve
    mc"Hey [s_name]."
    mc"Oh, you‚Äôve prepared dinner already!"
    show sc day3hoteldinner d10
    s"Yeah, I thought I‚Äôd try and have it ready for you by the time you finished your call."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d09
    s"Please, have a seat."
    mc"Okay, thanks again for this [s_name]."
    # (He sits down)"
    show sc day3hoteldinner d01
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3hoteldinner d01","sc day3hoteldinner d01x","v_pt_image_index_72")
    s"It‚Äôs my pleasure. Some wine to go with dinner?"
    mc"Yes, please."
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    # (Friend pours wine for him)"
    show sc day3hoteldinner d06
    s"So how did the rest of your chat with Nicole go?"
    show sc day3hoteldinner d02
    mc"It was okay. She has to be up early tomorrow morning and has a heap of paperwork and emails to go through tonight."
    mc"So Nicole thought it would be best to give me a call me now as she wouldn‚Äôt have had the time to later."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d01
    s"That was nice of her. She seems lovely."
    mc"Yeah, she does work very hard and even though she‚Äôs been incredibly stressed out of late, she didn‚Äôt let that show during the phone call."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d02
    mc"But she seemed to like you though."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d05
    s"Well, of course, I‚Äôm such a likeable person!"
    show sc day3hoteldinner d01
    mc"Haha, of course you are."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d02
    s"Does she have anyone back home to keep her company?"
    mc"She has a sister that doesn‚Äôt live too far from the city."
    mc"However, her Mom and Dad live several hours away and after that, it‚Äôs pretty much whoever she works with."
    mc"But any time she spends away from the office or in court, she mainly wants to spend with me."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d08
    s"(It doesn‚Äôt sound like she has many friends, which if true, is incredibly sad.)"
    s"(I hope she‚Äôs going to be okay without [y_name] being there for three months.)"
    show sc day3hoteldinner d02
    s"How do you think she‚Äôll fill her time without you there?"
    mc"You know, I‚Äôve been so occupied with everything I‚Äôve had to do since I arrived here that I haven‚Äôt really thought about it."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d03
    s"You should try and keep in touch with her [y_name] because it sounds like spending time with you when she‚Äôs not working is a huge deal for her."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d02
    mc"Well, we did promise to call each other every day and we‚Äôve pretty much done that so far."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d01
    s"That‚Äôs good."
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs nice that [s_name] is interested in my relationship with Nicole, but at the same time, it‚Äôs good to have a break from each other too.)"
    mc"(But now all I can think about is how Nicole is coping without me back home.)"
    show sc day3hoteldinner d04
    s"Try some of your dinner [y_name], you haven‚Äôt even touched it yet!"
    show sc day3hoteldinner d01
    mc"Oh right, sure thing [s_name]."
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (have less food in their bowls when the scene resumes)"
