    with dissolve
    s"So how was it, honestly?"
    # [It was great / Best dish]"
    menu:
        "It was great":
            show sc day3hoteldinner d12
            mc"It was great for the most part [s_name]."
            mc"The sauce was a little overbearing, but I guess that‚Äôs what the wine is for, to wash it down with."
            mc"The dish turned out pretty well."
            show sc day3hoteldinner d11
            s"Thanks [y_name]."
            show sc day3hoteldinner d07
            s"I mean, I‚Äôm by no means an experienced cook, but I chose this recipe because of the ingredients and ease of preparation."
            show sc day3hoteldinner d12
            mc"Well you could have fooled me."
            show sc day3hoteldinner d11
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,1,s_name)
            mc"That was almost as good as any dinner I‚Äôve had at home or in a restaurant." #+1 FRIEND Point"
        "Best dish"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc day3hoteldinner d12
            mc"Oh my god! That was like the best dish I‚Äôve had in ages!"
            show sc day3hoteldinner d08
            s"Oh come on, was it really that good?"
            show sc day3hoteldinner d12
            mc"Honestly [s_name], it was delicious!"
            show sc day3hoteldinner d14
            s"Thanks [y_name]."
            show sc day3hoteldinner d11
            s"I mean, I‚Äôm by no means an experienced cook, but I chose this recipe because of the ingredients and ease of preparation."
            mc"Well you could have fooled me."
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,2,s_name)
            mc"I don‚Äôt think I‚Äôve ever had an Italian dinner this good at home or in a restaurant." #+2 FRIEND Points"
            # (scene continues)"
    # (friend smiles)"
    show sc day3hoteldinner d06
    mc"I could have sworn that the fridge was almost empty when I had breakfast this morning."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d11
    s"That‚Äôs because I did a food shop while I was out and when Jazmin was doing window shopping for some designers she was interested in."
    s"I wanted dinner to be perfect, and to try and make up for last night‚Äôs fiasco."
    mc"Not that you had to [s_name], but you just about made a perfect dinner."
    show sc day3hoteldinner d11
    s"Some more wine?"
    mc"Oh, yes please!"
    # (Friend goes to pour some wine when her phone calls) Cell Phone Ring Sound Effect.mp3 to be added"
