label lb_day3_s_tv_together:
    # Day 3 (EOW) 22 - Friend and the MC watch TV together"
    # - tells her about having a better day"
    if _in_replay:
        if y_name == None:
            $ y_name = "MC"
        else:
            $ y_name = persistent.y_name

        if s_name == None:
            $ s_name = "S"
        else:
            $ s_name = persistent.s_name

        show screen toprightmenu

        play music "music/01/2936-fliegen-by-sascha-ende.mp3"


    scene sc day3game g01
    with dissolve
    mc"(Oh wow, I wonder what games they have here.)"
    show sc day3game g02
    mc"(It‚Äôs been a good six or seven years since I‚Äôve played any kind of console games.)"
    # (MC sits down and picks up a remote)"
    mc"(Why would [s_name] have these?)"
    # (friend enters the living room to find the MC playing an old video game he used to play as a kid)"
    show sc day3game g04
    s"Hmm, I see you found the controllers for the GameStation."
    show sc day3game g08
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3game g08","sc day3game g08x","v_pt_image_index_73")
    mc"(Gulp!)"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    if renpy.loadable("extras.animations") and persistent.v_anim_enabled:
        window hide
        scene wip_02_s_minigame  at tt_top
        pause
        window show
    else:
        show sc day3game g05
    mc"Yeah I was about to check out the games you have. Why do you have these?"
    show sc day3game g06
    s"We used to have it set up in the games room for guests but then moved it into here when we re-painted that room a few weeks ago."
    show sc day3game g04
    s"[c_name] also set it up on this TV because she actually enjoys playing some of those games."
    show sc day3game g05
    mc"Really?"
    s"Yeah, she‚Äôs a bit of a game nut!"
    show sc day3game g03
    mc"Did you want to play with me, or maybe we could see what movies are on TV tonight?"
    show sc day3game g07
    s"Well video games were never my thing as you may remember. And I‚Äôm not really in the mood for watching any TV."
    show sc day3game g05
    s"How about we do something else?"
    show sc day3game g04
    mc"All right, what did you have in mind?"
    s"Let‚Äôs play something really old school, like a board game perhaps?"
    show sc day3game g03
    mc"Oh, are you serious?"
    show sc day3game g04
    s"Come on, it‚Äôll be fun!"
    show sc day3game g05
    mc"Okay, why the hell not! So what games do you have? "
    s"Well, my favourite was always ‚ÄúGuess That Person‚Äù, which we just so happen to have!"
    show sc day3game g09
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day3game g09b","v_rewards_s_21")
    s"Where is it? Hmm..."
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day3game g10
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc day3game g10","sc day3game g10x","v_pt_image_index_74")
    s"Here it is!"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc day3game g11
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    show sc day3game g67
    mc"Okay, but what are we playing for?"
    show sc day3game g12
    s"Huh?"
    mc"Well the winner should get something special, don‚Äôt you think?"
    show sc day3game g14
    s"Yes, I agree. Okay, what should we bet on?"
    show sc day3game g20
    mc"How about‚Ä¶ Whoever wins gets the rest of this wine?"
    show sc day3game g16
    s"(Hmm‚Ä¶ [y_name] sure likes to have a drink. That‚Äôs his fourth glass of wine already.)"
    show sc day3game g19
    s"Um, how about we make it a bit more interesting?"
    show sc day3game g13
    s"Punishment for the loser."
    show sc day3game g14
    mc"Okay, what should the punishment be for losing then?"
    show sc day3game g13
    s"All right, if I win, you have to tell me your most embarrassing sexual story."
    s"But if I lose, then I have to tell you mine."
    show sc day3game g14
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Would we be pushing the boundaries of our relationship if I agree to this?)"
    mc"(Well, it‚Äôs not like we‚Äôre kids anymore, we‚Äôre adults, and we should be able to share these kind of stories with each other.)"
    mc"Okay, deal!"
    show sc day3game g12
    mc"However, how will I know that you‚Äôre telling the truth if you happen to lose?"
    show sc day3game g14
    s"You‚Äôre going to have to trust me on this one [y_name]."
    show sc day3game g13
    s"And even if I‚Äôm lying, I promise the story that I tell you is one that you‚Äôll probably find really funny, and you will be thinking about it all night long."
    show sc day3game g14
    mc"(Woah! She‚Äôs obviously thought this out beforehand. I don‚Äôt really want to tell her my most embarrassing story so I better win this damn game!)"
    mc"Okay, you‚Äôre on. Shall we start then?"
    s"Yes we can. How about we start by setting up the characters and choosing one for the other person to guess."
    show sc day3game g18
    s"Once we‚Äôve done that, I‚Äôll tell you the set rules for the way I play ‚ÄúGuess That Person‚Äù."
    show sc day3game g14
    mc"Sounds good."
    mc"(Now I just have to think of what player I‚Äôm going to choose.)"
    show sc day3game g21
    s"Okay, are you ready for me to go through the rules [y_name]?"
    show sc day3game g14
    mc"Yep, fire away!"
    s"All right, so there‚Äôs one main rule that is a little different when it comes to asking your opponent questions."
    s"As you know, you have to ask questions for your opponent to give either a ‚ÄúYes‚Äù or a ‚ÄúNo‚Äù as a response."
    s"However, the only question that you are not allowed to ask is if the mystery character that your opponent has chosen is male, or female."
    s"And you can‚Äôt bend that rule by asking any alternate questions like ‚ÄúDoes your character have boobs or a penis?‚Äù"
    s"Is that fair enough?"
    mc"Haha, yep, sounds good to me."
    show sc day3game g18
    s"Okay, and as with the normal rules, if you decide to guess the opponent‚Äôs card, and it‚Äôs wrong, then you automatically lose the game."
    show sc day3game g14
    s"So choose wisely."
    mc"Of course."
    show sc day3game g21
    s"So choose your mystery character for me to try and guess [y_name], and I will do the same for the character of mine that you have to guess."
    # (MC looks over his board)"
    show sc day3game g22
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ This guy will do.)"
    mc"(He‚Äôs an interesting looking dude. That beard makes him look like the ultra-suspicious type though...)"
    show sc day3game g14
    mc"Okay, I‚Äôve chosen my mystery character."
    s"As have I."
    mc"So who goes first?"
    show sc day3game g13
    s"According to the rules, the youngest person goes first. Looks like that‚Äôs me! Haha!"
    show sc day3game g14
    mc"How very convenient."
    s"Okay, so my first question is‚Ä¶"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # On the screen - A Little While Later‚Ä¶"
    scene sc day3game g23
    with dissolve
    mc"(All right, six possible options to go, and they‚Äôre all women.)"
    mc"(Seems to be a running theme around here at the moment.)"
    mc"(Okay, I have to eliminate a few of these before I even contemplate making any guesses.)"
    # (MC pours some more wine into his glass)"
    show sc day3game g25
    mc"More for you [s_name]?"
    show sc day3game g17
    s"Uh, no thanks. I‚Äôm good."
    show sc day3game g13
    s"Maybe you should ease up on the wine [y_name]. We want to be able to finish the game before you pass out!"
    show sc day3game g27
    mc"I‚Äôm fine [s_name]. Now what‚Äôs the next question that you‚Äôre going to ask me?"
    show sc day3game g15
    s"Um, it‚Äôs not my turn [y_name], it‚Äôs yours."
    show sc day3game g28
    mc"Oh, right‚Ä¶ Of course it is!"
    show sc day3game g26
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Maybe she‚Äôs right, perhaps I have had too much to drink.)"
    s"(And I thought that I was forgetful when I‚Äôve had too much to drink. At least it‚Äôs not just me that has a little problem with alcohol.)"
    show sc day3game g12
    jump lb_day3_s_tv_together_1

